# <a name="sensitive-information-type-entity-definitions"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-104">Определения типов конфиденциальной информации</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-104">Sensitive information type entity definitions</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-105">Защита от потери данных (DLP) в центре соответствия требованиям включает множество типов конфиденциальной информации, готовых к использованию в политиках защиты от потери данных.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-105">Data loss prevention (DLP) in the Compliance Center includes many sensitive information types that are ready for you to use in your DLP policies.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-106">В этой статье перечислены все эти типы конфиденциальной информации и показано, каким именно образом политика защиты от потери данных выявляет каждый тип.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-106">This topic lists all of these sensitive information types and shows what a DLP policy looks for when it detects each type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-107">Тип конфиденциальной информации определяется шаблоном, который можно идентифицировать регулярным выражением или функцией.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-107">A sensitive information type is defined by a pattern that can be identified by a regular expression or a function.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-108">Кроме того, для идентификации типа конфиденциальной информации могут использоваться подкрепляющие доказательства, такие как ключевые слова и контрольные суммы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-108">In addition, corroborative evidence such as keywords and checksums can be used to identify a sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-109">Уровень вероятности и расположение слов и знаков также используются в процессе оценки.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-109">Confidence level and proximity are also used in the evaluation process.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-110">Для типов конфиденциальной информации требуется одна из следующих подписок:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-110">Sensitive information types require one of these subscriptions:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-111">Microsoft 365 E3</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-111">Microsoft 365 E3</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-112">Microsoft 365 E5</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-112">Microsoft 365 E5</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-113">Типы конфиденциальной информации можно использовать в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-113">Sensitive information types can be used in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-114">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-114">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-115">соответствие требованиям полЦиес</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-115">communication compliance polcies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-116">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-116">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-117">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-117">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-118">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-118">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

  
## <a name="aba-routing-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-119">Номер маршрутизации код банка ABA</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-119">ABA routing number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-120">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-120">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-121">девять цифр, которые могут быть в форматированном или неформатированном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-121">nine digits which may be in a formatted or unformatted pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-122">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-122">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-123">Форматируемые</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-123">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-124">четыре цифры, начинающиеся с 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7 или 8.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-124">four digits beginning with 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7, or 8</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-125">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-125">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-126">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-126">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-127">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-127">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-128">цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-128">a digit</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-129">Неформатированный: девять последовательных цифр, начиная с 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7 или 8.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-129">Unformatted: nine consecutive digits beginning with 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7, or 8</span></span> 

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-130">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-130">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-131">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-131">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-132">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-132">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-133">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-133">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-134">функция Func_aba_routing находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-134">The function Func_aba_routing finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-135">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ABA_Routing.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-135">A keyword from Keyword_ABA_Routing is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- ABA Routing Number -->
<Entity id="cb353f78-2b72-4c3c-8827-92ebe4f69fdf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_aba_routing" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ABA_Routing" />
      </Pattern>
 </Entity>
```

## <a name="argentina-national-identity-dni-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-155">Внутренний идентификационный номер (DNI), Аргентина</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-155">Argentina national identity (DNI) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-156">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-156">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-157">Восемь цифр, разделенных точками.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-157">Eight digits separated by periods</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-158">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-158">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-159">Восемь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-159">Eight digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-160">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-160">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-161">точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-161">a period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-162">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-162">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-163">точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-163">a period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-164">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-164">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-165">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-165">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-166">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-166">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-167">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-167">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-168">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-168">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-169">регулярное выражение Regex_argentina_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-169">The regular expression Regex_argentina_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-170">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_argentina_national_id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-170">A keyword from Keyword_argentina_national_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Argentina National Identity (DNI) Number -->
<Entity id="eefbb00e-8282-433c-8620-8f1da3bffdb2" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Regex_argentina_national_id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_argentina_national_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-171">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-171">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_argentina_national_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-172">Keyword_argentina_national_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-172">Keyword_argentina_national_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-173">Argentina National Identity number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-173">Argentina National Identity number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-174">Удостоверение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-174">Identity</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-175">Идентификация национальной идентификационной карточки</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-175">Identification National Identity Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-176">DNI</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-176">DNI</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-177">Национальная реестр пользователей NIC</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-177">NIC National Registry of Persons</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-178">Documento Nacional de Identidad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-178">Documento Nacional de Identidad</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-179">Registro Nacional de las Personas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-179">Registro Nacional de las Personas</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-180">идентидад</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-180">Identidad</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-181">идентификаЦиóн</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-181">Identificación</span></span> 
   
## <a name="australia-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-182">Номер банковского счета для Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-182">Australia bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-183">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-183">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-184">шесть – ТВН цифрами с номером филиала банка или без него</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-184">six to twn digits with or without a bank state branch number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-185">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-185">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-186">Номер счета — от шести до десяти цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-186">Account number is six to ten digits.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-187">Номер филиала государственного банка Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-187">Australia bank state branch number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-188">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-188">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-189">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-189">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-190">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-190">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-191">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-191">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-192">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-192">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-193">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-193">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-194">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-194">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-195">регулярное выражение Regex_australia_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-195">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern..</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-196">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_australia_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-196">A keyword from Keyword_australia_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-197">регулярное выражение Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-197">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-198">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-198">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-199">регулярное выражение Regex_australia_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-199">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern..</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-200">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_australia_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-200">A keyword from Keyword_australia_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Australia Bank Account Number -->
```

## <a name="australia-business-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-216">Бизнес-номер Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-216">Australia business number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-217">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-217">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-218">11 цифр с необязательными ограничителями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-218">11 digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-219">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-219">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-220">11 цифр с необязательными ограничителями:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-220">11 digits with optional delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-221">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-221">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-222">Необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-222">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-223">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-223">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-224">Необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-224">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-225">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-225">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-226">Необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-226">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-227">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-227">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-228">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-228">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-229">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-229">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-230">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-230">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-231">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-231">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-232">Функция Func_australian_business_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-232">The function Func_australian_business_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-233">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_australian_business_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-233">A keyword from Keywords_australian_business_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-234">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-234">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-235">Функция Func_australian_business_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-235">The function Func_australian_business_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Australia Business Number -->
      <Entity id="76e83b3b-01ee-4530-aced-e667a6609f49" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_business_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_australian_business_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_business_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="australia-company-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-245">Номер компании Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-245">Australia company number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-246">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-246">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-247">девять цифр с разделителями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-247">nine digits with delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-248">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-248">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-249">девять цифр с разделителями:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-249">nine digits with delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-250">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-250">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-251">пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-251">a space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-252">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-252">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-253">пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-253">a space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-254">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-254">three digits</span></span>


### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-255">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-255">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-256">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-256">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-257">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-257">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-258">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-258">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-259">Функция Func_Australian_Company_Number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-259">The function Func_Australian_Company_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-260">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_Australian_Company_Number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-260">A keyword from Keyword_Australian_Company_Number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-261">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-261">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-262">Функция Func_Australian_Company_Number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-262">The function Func_Australian_Company_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Australia Company Number -->
      <Entity id="b1fba4f7-7b3e-4bb9-8f9a-9366df604dbb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Australian_Company_Number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Australian_Company_Number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Australian_Company_Number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="australia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-272">Номер водительского удостоверения для Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-272">Australia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-273">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-273">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-274">девять букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-274">nine letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-275">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-275">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-276">девять букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-276">nine letters and digits:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-277">две цифры или буквы (без учета регистра).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-277">two digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-278">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-278">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-279">пять цифр или букв (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-279">five digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-280">OR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-280">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-281">один-два необязательных буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-281">one to two optional letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-282">от четырех до девяти цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-282">four to nine digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-283">OR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-283">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-284">девять цифр или букв (без учета регистра);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-284">nine digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-285">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-285">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-286">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-286">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-287">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-287">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-288">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-288">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-289">регулярное выражение Regex_australia_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-289">The regular expression Regex_australia_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-290">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-290">A keyword from Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-291">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions не находится.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-291">No keyword from Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Australia Drivers License Number -->
<Entity id="1cbbc8f5-9216-4392-9eb5-5ac2298d1356" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-298">дриверлиценцес</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-298">DriverLicences</span></span>

## <a name="australia-medical-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-391">Номер медицинской учетной записи Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-391">Australia medical account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-392">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-392">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-393">10–11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-393">10-11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-394">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-394">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-395">10–11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-395">10-11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-396">Первая цифра находится в диапазоне 2-6</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-396">first digit is in the range 2-6</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-397">девятая цифра — это контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-397">ninth digit is a check digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-398">Десятая цифра — это цифра, связанная с вопросом</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-398">tenth digit is the issue digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-399">Одиннадцатая цифра (необязательно) — индивидуальный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-399">eleventh digit (optional) is the individual number</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-400">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-400">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-401">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-401">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-402">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-402">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-403">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-403">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-404">функция Func_australian_medical_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-404">The function Func_australian_medical_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-405">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-405">A keyword from Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-406">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-406">The checksum passes.</span></span>


```xml
  <!-- Australia Medical Account Number -->
<Entity id="104a99a0-3d3b-4542-a40d-ab0b9e1efe63" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_medical_account_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number"/>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-409">bank account details</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-409">bank account details</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-410">medicare payments</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-410">medicare payments</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-411">mortgage account</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-411">mortgage account</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-412">bank payments</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-412">bank payments</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-413">information branch</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-413">information branch</span></span>

## <a name="australia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-418">Номер паспорта для Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-418">Australia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-419">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-419">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-420">Буква, за которой следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-420">A letter followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-421">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-421">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-422">Буква (без учета регистра), за которой следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-422">A letter (not case sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-423">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-423">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-424">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-424">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-425">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-425">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-426">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-426">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-427">регулярное выражение Regex_australia_passport_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-427">The regular expression Regex_australia_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-428">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_passport или Keyword_australia_passport_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-428">A keyword from Keyword_passport or Keyword_australia_passport_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Australia Passport Number -->
<Entity id="29869db6-602d-4853-ab93-3484f905df50" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_passport_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_passport_number" />
        </Any>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>   
```

## <a name="australia-tax-file-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-462">Номер файла налога для Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-462">Australia tax file number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-463">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-463">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-464">от восьми до девяти цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-464">eight to nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-465">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-465">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-466">от восьми до девяти цифр, как правило, представляются пробелы следующим образом:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-466">eight to nine digits typically presented with spaces as follows:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-467">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-467">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-468">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-468">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-469">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-469">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-470">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-470">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-471">две и три цифры, где последняя цифра — проверочная.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-471">two to three digits where the last digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-472">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-472">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-473">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-473">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-474">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-474">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-475">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-475">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-476">функция Func_australian_tax_file_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-476">The function Func_australian_tax_file_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-477">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number или Keyword_number_exclusions не найдено;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-477">No keyword from Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number or Keyword_number_exclusions is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-478">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-478">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
   <!-- Australia Tax File Number -->
    <Entity id="e29bc95f-ff70-4a37-aa01-04d17360a4c5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_tax_file_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-490">Номер водительского удостоверения для Австрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-490">Austria driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-491">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-491">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-492">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-492">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-493">восемь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-493">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-494">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-494">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-495">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-495">eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-496">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-496">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-497">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-497">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-498">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-498">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-499">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-499">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-500">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-500">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-501">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-501">A keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
<!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-identity-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-518">Австрийская идентификационная карточка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-518">Austria identity card</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-519">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-519">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-520">24 – символическое сочетание букв, цифр и специальных символов;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-520">A 24-character combination of letters, digits, and special characters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-521">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-521">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-522">24 символа:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-522">24 characters:</span></span>
  
-  <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-523">22 буквы (без учета регистра), цифры, обратные косые черты, косые черты и знаки плюса</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-523">22 letters (not case-sensitive), digits, backslashes, forward slashes, or plus signs</span></span> 
    
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-524">две буквы (без учета регистра), цифры, обратные косые черты, знаки косой черты, знаки плюса и знаки равенства.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-524">two letters (not case-sensitive), digits, backslashes, forward slashes, plus signs, or equal signs</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-525">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-525">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-526">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-526">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-527">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-527">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-528">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-528">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-529">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-529">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-530">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-530">A keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
   
```xml
      <!-- Austria Identity Card -->
```

## <a name="austria-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-536">Номер паспорта для Австрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-536">Austria passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-537">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе сенситивеинформатион Passport Number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-537">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitiveinformation type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-538">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-538">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-539">Одна буква, за которой следует необязательный пробел и семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-539">One letter followed by an optional space and seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-540">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-540">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-541">Сочетание одной буквы, семи цифр и одного пробела:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-541">A combination of one letter, seven digits, and one space:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-542">одна буква (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-542">one letter (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-543">один пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-543">one space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-544">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-544">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-545">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-545">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-546">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-546">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-547">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-547">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-548">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-548">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-549">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-549">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-550">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-550">A keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-551">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-551">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_austria_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-552">Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-552">Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-553">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-553">passport number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-555">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-555">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-556">реисепасс</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-556">reisepass</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-557">öстерреичисч реисепасс</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-557">österreichisch reisepass</span></span>

## <a name="austria-social-security-number-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-558">Австрийский номер социального страхования или эквивалентная идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-558">Austria social security number or equivalent identification</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-559">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в номере социального страхования ЕС или эквивалентного идентификатора.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-559">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-560">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-560">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-561">10 цифр в указанном формате</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-561">10 digits in the specified format</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-562">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-562">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-563">10 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-563">10 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-564">три цифры, соответствующие серийному номеру.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-564">three digits that correspond to a serial number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-565">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-565">one check digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-566">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (ДДММГГ —)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-566">six digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMYY)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-567">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-567">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-568">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-568">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-569">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-569">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-570">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-570">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-571">Функция "Func_austria_eu_</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-571">The function  \`Func_austria_eu_</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-572">_or_equivalent ' находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-572">_or_equivalent\` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-573">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-573">a keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-574">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-574">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-575">Функция  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-575">The function  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU SSN or Equivalent Number -->
<Entity id="d24e32a4-c0bb-4ba8-899d-6303b95742d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
            <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-591">Налоговый идентификационный номер для Австрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-591">Austria tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-592">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-592">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-593">девять цифр с необязательным дефисом и косой чертой.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-593">nine digits with optional hyphen and forward slash</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-594">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-594">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-595">девять цифр с необязательным дефисом и косой чертой.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-595">nine digits with optional hyphen and forward slash:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-596">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-596">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-597">дефис (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-597">a hyphen (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-598">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-598">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-599">косая черта (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-599">a forward slash (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-600">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-600">four digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-601">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-601">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-602">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-602">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-603">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-603">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-604">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-604">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-605">Функция  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-605">The function  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-606">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-606">A keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-607">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-607">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-608">Функция  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-608">The function  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Austria Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="4fd58d22-af28-4451-b18a-6f722430a56d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-617">налог без #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-617">tax no#</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-621">такси #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-621">taxid#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-622">таксидно #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-622">taxidno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-623">таксиднумбер #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-623">taxidnumber#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-624">таксно #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-624">taxno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-625">такснумбер #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-625">taxnumber#</span></span>

## <a name="austria-value-added-tax"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-631">Налог на добавленную стоимость (Австрия)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-631">Austria value added tax</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-632">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-632">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-633">11-буквенно-буквенно-буквенный шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-633">11-character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-634">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-634">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-635">11-буквенно-цифровой буквенно-значный шаблон:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-635">11-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-636">A или a</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-636">A or a</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-637">T или t</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-637">T or t</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-638">Необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-638">Optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-639">U или u</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-639">U or u</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-640">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-640">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-641">две или три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-641">two or three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-642">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-642">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-643">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-643">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-644">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-644">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-645">одна или две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-645">one or two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-646">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-646">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-647">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-647">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-648">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-648">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-649">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-649">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-650">Функция Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-650">The function Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-651">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_Austria_Value_Added_Tax.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-651">A keyword from Keyword_Austria_Value_Added_Tax is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-652">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-652">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-653">Функция Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-653">The function Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Austria Value Added Tax -->
      <Entity id="b6a3eda2-c56c-4b69-a5f7-dca34db00f48" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Austria_Value_Added_Tax" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-659">НДС номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-659">vat no.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-660">ватно #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-660">vatno#</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-667">умсатзстеуер — идентификатионснуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-667">umsatzsteuer-identifikationsnummer</span></span>

## <a name="azure-documentdb-auth-key"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-671">Ключ проверки подлинности Azure DocumentDB</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-671">Azure DocumentDB auth key</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-672">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-672">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-673">Строка "DocumentDb", за которой следуют символы и строки, описанные в приведенном ниже шаблоне.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-673">The string "DocumentDb" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-674">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-674">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-675">Строка "DocumentDb"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-675">The string "DocumentDb"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-676">Любая комбинация из 3-200 прописных или строчных букв, цифр, символов, специальных символов и пробелов.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-676">Any combination of between 3-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-677">Символ "больше" (>), знак равенства (=), кавычки (") или апостроф (')</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-677">A greater than symbol (>), an equal sign (=), a quotation mark ("), or an apostrophe (')</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-678">Любая комбинация 86 строчных или прописных букв, цифр, символов косой черты (/) или знака плюса (+).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-678">Any combination of 86 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-679">Два знака равенства (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-679">Two equal signs (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-680">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-680">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-681">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-681">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-682">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-682">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-683">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-683">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-684">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureDocumentDBAuthKey находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-684">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureDocumentDBAuthKey finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-685">Регулярное выражение CEP_CommonExampleKeywords не **находит содержимое** , которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-685">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords does **not** find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Azure Document DB Auth Key -->
<Entity id="0f587d92-eb28-44a9-bd1c-90f2892b47aa" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureDocumentDBAuthKey" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
          </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-702">Строка "Server", "Server" или "Data Source", за которой следуют символы и строки, описанные в приведенном ниже шаблоне, в том числе строку "клаудапп. Azure".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-702">The string "Server", "server", or "data source" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the string "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-703">com "или" клаудапп. Azure.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-703">com" or "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-704">NET "или" Database. ### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-706">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-706">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-707">строка "Server", "Server" или "Data Source"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-707">the string "Server", "server", or "data source"</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-711">Любая комбинация из 1-200 прописных или строчных букв, цифр, символов, специальных символов и пробелов.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-711">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-712">Строка "клаудапп. Azure.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-712">The string "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-713">com "," клаудапп. Azure.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-713">com", "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-714">NET "или" Database. - <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-716">Любая комбинация из 1-300 прописных или строчных букв, цифр, символов, специальных символов и пробелов.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-716">any combination of between 1-300 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-717">строка "Password", "Password" или "pwd"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-717">the string "Password", "password", or "pwd"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-718">ноль — два символа пробела</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-718">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-719">знак равенства (=);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-719">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-720">ноль — два символа пробела</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-720">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-721">один или несколько символов, не отделяющая точку с запятой (;), кавычки (") или апостроф (')</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-721">one or more characters that is not a semicolon (;), quotation mark ("), or apostrophe (')</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-722">точка с запятой (;), кавычки (") или апостроф (')</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-722">a semicolon (;), quotation mark ("), or apostrophe (')</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-723">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-723">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-724">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-724">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-725">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-725">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-726">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-726">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-728">Регулярное выражение CEP_CommonExampleKeywords не **находит содержимое** , которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-728">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords does **not** find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml

<Entity id="ce1a126d-186f-4700-8c0c-486157b953fd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">

        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-iot-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-743">Строка подключения Azure IoT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-743">Azure IoT connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-744">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-744">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-745">Строка "HostName", за которой следуют символы и строки, описанные в приведенном ниже шаблоне, включая строки "Azure — Devices.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-745">The string "HostName" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the strings "azure-devices.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-746">NET "и" Шаредакцесскэй ".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-746">net" and "SharedAccessKey".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-747">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-747">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-748">строка "HostName"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-748">the string "HostName"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-749">ноль — два символа пробела</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-749">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-750">знак равенства (=);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-750">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-751">ноль — два символа пробела</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-751">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-752">Любая комбинация из 1-200 прописных или строчных букв, цифр, символов, специальных символов и пробелов.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-752">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-753">строка "Azure — Devices.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-753">the string "azure-devices.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-754">команде</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-754">net"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-755">Любая комбинация из 1-200 прописных или строчных букв, цифр, символов, специальных символов и пробелов.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-755">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-756">строка "Шаредакцесскэй"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-756">the string "SharedAccessKey"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-757">ноль — два символа пробела</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-757">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-758">знак равенства (=);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-758">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-759">ноль — два символа пробела</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-759">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-760">Любая комбинация 43 строчных или прописных букв, цифр, символов косой черты (/) или знака плюса (+).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-760">any combination of 43 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-761">знак равенства (=);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-761">an equal sign (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-762">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-762">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-763">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-763">No</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-765">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-765">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

```xml

        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureIoTConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-826">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-826">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-827">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureRedisCacheConnectionString находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону..</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-827">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureRedisCacheConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern..</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-828">Регулярное выражение CEP_CommonExampleKeywords не **находит содержимое** , которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-828">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords does **not** find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml

<Entity id="095a7e6c-efd8-46d5-af7b-5298d53a49fc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">

        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
