## <a name="azure-sas"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-843">SAS Azure</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-843">Azure SAS</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-844">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-844">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-845">Строка "SIG", за которой следуют символы и строки, описанные в приведенном ниже шаблоне.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-845">The string "sig" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-846">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-846">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-847">строка "SIG"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-847">the string "sig"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-848">ноль — два символа пробела</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-848">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-849">знак равенства (=);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-849">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-850">ноль — два символа пробела</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-850">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-851">любое сочетание 43-53 символов, которые являются буквами нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифрами или знаком процента (%)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-851">any combination of between 43-53 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, or the percent sign (%)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-852">строка "% 3D"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-852">the string "%3d"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-853">любой символ, который не является буквой нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифрой или знаком процента (%)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-853">any character that is not a lower- or uppercase letter, digit, or percent sign (%)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-854">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-854">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-855">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-855">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-856">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-856">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-857">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-857">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-858">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureSAS находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-858">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureSAS finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure SAS-->
<Entity id="4d235014-e564-47f4-a6fb-6ebb4a826834" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureSAS" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-874">знак равенства (=);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-874">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-875">ноль — два символа пробела</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-875">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-881">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-881">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-901">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-901">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-902">строка "Дефаултендпоинтспротокол"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-902">the string "DefaultEndpointsProtocol"</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-908">ноль — два символа пробела</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-908">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-909">знак равенства (=);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-909">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-910">ноль — два символа пробела</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-910">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-915">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-915">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-916">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-916">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-917">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKey находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-917">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKey finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-918">Регулярное выражение CEP_AzureEmulatorStorageAccountFilter не **находит содержимое** , которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-918">The regular expression CEP_AzureEmulatorStorageAccountFilter does **not** find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-919">Регулярное выражение CEP_CommonExampleKeywords не **находит содержимое** , которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-919">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords does **not** find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure Storage Account Key-->
<Entity id="c7bc98e8-551a-4c35-a92d-d2c8cda714a7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKey" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_AzureEmulatorStorageAccountFilter" />
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-storage-account-key-generic"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-937">Ключ учетной записи хранилища Azure (общий)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-937">Azure Storage account key (generic)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-938">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-938">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-939">Любая комбинация 86 строчных или прописных букв, цифр, знаков косой черты (/) или знака плюса (+) перед или за ними следуют символы, указанные в приведенном ниже шаблоне.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-939">Any combination of 86 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, the forward slash (/), or plus sign (+), preceded or followed by the characters outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-940">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-940">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-941">ноль к одному символу "больше" (>), апостроф ('), знак равенства (=), кавычки (") или решетку (#)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-941">zero to one of the greater than symbol (>), apostrophe ('), equal sign (=), quotation mark ("), or number sign (#)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-942">любое сочетание 86 символов, которые представляют собой буквы в нижнем или верхнем регистре, цифры, косую черту (/) или знак плюса (+).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-942">any combination of 86 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, the forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-943">два знака равенства (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-943">two equal signs (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-944">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-944">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-945">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-945">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-946">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-946">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-947">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-947">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-948">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKeyGeneric находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-948">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKeyGeneric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure Storage Account Key (Generic)-->
<Entity id="7ff41bd0-5419-4523-91d6-383b3a37f084" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKeyGeneric" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
## <a name="belgium-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-949">Номер водительского удостоверения для бельгийского драйвера</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-949">Belgium driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-950">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-950">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-951">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-951">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-952">десять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-952">ten digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-953">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-953">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-954">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-954">ten digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-955">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-955">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-956">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-956">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-957">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-957">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-958">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-958">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-959">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-959">The regular expression  `Regex_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-960">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-960">A keyword from  `Keywords_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-962">**Keywords__belgium_eu_driver "s_license_number**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-962">**Keywords__belgium_eu_driver's_license_number**</span></span>

## <a name="belgium-national-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-982">Бельгийский национальный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-982">Belgium national number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-983">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-983">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-984">11 цифр, а также необязательные разделители</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-984">11 digits plus optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-985">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-985">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-986">11 цифр, а также разделители:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-986">11 digits plus delimiters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-987">шесть цифр и две дополнительные точки в формате гг. Мм. DD для даты рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-987">six digits and two optional periods in the format YY.MM.DD for date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-988">Необязательный разделитель из точки, тире, пробела</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-988">An optional delimiter from dot, dash, space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-989">три последовательные цифры (нечетные для мужчин, даже для женщин).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-989">three sequential digits (odd for males, even for females)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-990">Необязательный разделитель из точки, тире, пробела</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-990">An optional delimiter from dot, dash, space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-991">две контрольные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-991">two check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-992">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-992">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-993">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-993">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-994">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-994">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-995">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-995">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-996">функция Func_belgium_national_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-996">The function Func_belgium_national_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-997">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_belgium_national_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-997">A keyword from Keyword_belgium_national_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-998">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-998">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-999">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-999">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1000">функция Func_belgium_national_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1000">The function Func_belgium_national_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1001">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1001">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Belgium National Number -->
       <Entity id="fb969c9e-0fd1-4b18-8091-a2123c5e6a54" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_national_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_belgium_national_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_national_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="belgium-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1060">Номер паспорта Бельгии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1060">Belgium passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1061">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1061">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1062">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1062">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1063">две буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1063">two letters followed by six digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1064">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1064">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1065">две буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1065">two letters and followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1066">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1066">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1067">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1067">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1068">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1068">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1069">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1069">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1070">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1070">The regular expression  `Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1071">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1071">A keyword from  `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_belgium__eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1072">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1072">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1074">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1074">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1075">Бельгийский номер паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1075">belgian passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1076">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1076">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1077">паспурт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1077">paspoort</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1078">паспуртнуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1078">paspoortnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1079">реисепасс Кеин</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1079">reisepass kein</span></span>

## <a name="belgium-social-security-number-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1081">Бельгийский номер социального страхования или идентификатор эквивалентной идентификации</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1081">Belgium social security number or equivalent identification</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1082">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в номере социального страхования ЕС или эквивалентного идентификатора.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1082">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1083">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1083">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1084">11 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1084">11 digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1085">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1085">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1086">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1086">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1087">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1087">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1088">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1088">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1089">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1089">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1090">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1090">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1091">Функция  `Func_belgium_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1091">The function  `Func_belgium_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1092">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_belgium_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1092">A keyword from  `Keywords_belgium_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1093">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1093">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1094">Функция  `Func_belgium_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1094">The function  `Func_belgium_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU SSN or Equivalent Number -->
<Entity id="d24e32a4-c0bb-4ba8-899d-6303b95742d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern> 
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>      
</Entity>
```

## <a name="belgium-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1114">Налоговый номер добавленной стоимости (Бельгия)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1114">Belgium value added tax number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1115">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1115">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1116">12-буквенно-буквенно-буквенный шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1116">12-character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1117">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1117">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1118">12-буквенно-буквенно-символьный шаблон:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1118">12-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1119">буква B или b</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1119">a letter B or b</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1120">буква E или e</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1120">a letter E or e</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1121">цифра 0</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1121">a digit 0</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1122">цифра от 1 до 9</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1122">a digit from 1 to 9</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1123">Необязательная точка или дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1123">an optional dot or Hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1124">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1124">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1125">Необязательная точка или дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1125">an optional dot or Hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1126">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1126">four digits</span></span>


### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1127">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1127">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1128">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1128">Yes</span></span>


### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1129">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1129">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1130">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1130">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1131">Функция Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1131">The function Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1132">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_belgium_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1132">A keyword from Keywords_belgium_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1133">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1133">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1134">Функция Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1134">The function Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Belgium Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="85b5b3c3-f2de-4ae8-ac46-fd3cb38bf9ed" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
    </Version>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1135">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1135">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_belgium_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1136">Keyword_belgium_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1136">Keyword_belgium_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1137">n º тва</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1137">nº tva</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1138">номер НДС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1138">vat number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1139">НДС No</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1139">vat no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1140">нумéро t. v. a</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1140">numéro t.v.a</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1141">умсатзстеуер — идентификатионснуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1141">umsatzsteuer-identifikationsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1142">умсатзстеуернуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1142">umsatzsteuernummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1143">бтв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1143">btw</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1144">бтв #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1144">btw#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1145">процент #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1145">vat#</span></span>


## <a name="brazil-cpf-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1146">Номер CPF для Бразилии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1146">Brazil CPF number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1147">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1147">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1148">11 цифр, которые включают проверочную цифру и могут быть форматированными или неформатированными.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1148">11 digits that include a check digit and can be formatted or unformatted</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1149">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1149">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1150">Форматируемые</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1150">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1151">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1151">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1152">точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1152">a period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1153">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1153">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1154">точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1154">a period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1155">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1155">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1156">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1156">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1157">две цифры, которые проверяются</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1157">two digits which are check digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1158">Неформатированные</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1158">Unformatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1159">11 цифр, где две последние цифры — проверочные.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1159">11 digits where the last two digits are check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1160">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1160">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1161">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1161">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1162">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1162">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1163">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1163">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1164">функция Func_brazil_cpf находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1164">The function Func_brazil_cpf finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1165">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_brazil_cpf;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1165">A keyword from Keyword_brazil_cpf is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1166">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1166">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1167">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1167">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1168">функция Func_brazil_cpf находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1168">The function Func_brazil_cpf finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1169">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1169">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Brazil CPF Number -->
<Entity id="78e09124-f2c3-4656-b32a-c1a132cd2711" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cpf"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_brazil_cpf"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cpf"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1170">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1170">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_brazil_cpf"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1171">Keyword_brazil_cpf</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1171">Keyword_brazil_cpf</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1172">CPF</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1172">CPF</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1173">Процедура</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1173">Identification</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1174">Registration</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1174">Registration</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1175">Реализации</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1175">Revenue</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1176">Cadastro de Pessoas Físicas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1176">Cadastro de Pessoas Físicas</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1177">импосто</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1177">Imposto</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1178">идентификаçãо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1178">Identificação</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1179">инскриçãо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1179">Inscrição</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1180">рецеита</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1180">Receita</span></span> 

   
## <a name="brazil-legal-entity-number-cnpj"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1181">Номер юридического лица в Бразилии (CNPJ)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1181">Brazil legal entity number (CNPJ)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1182">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1182">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1183">14 цифр, которые включают регистрационный номер, номер филиала и проверочные цифры, а также разделители.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1183">14 digits that include a registration number, branch number, and check digits, plus delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1184">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1184">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1185">14 цифр, а также разделители:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1185">14 digits, plus delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1186">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1186">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1187">точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1187">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1188">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1188">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1189">точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1189">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1190">три цифры (эти первые восемь цифр — регистрационный номер).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1190">three digits (these first eight digits are the registration number)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1191">косая черта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1191">a forward slash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1192">номер филиала из четырех цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1192">four-digit branch number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1193">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1193">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1194">две цифры, которые проверяются</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1194">two digits which are check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1195">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1195">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1196">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1196">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1197">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1197">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1198">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1198">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1199">функция Func_brazil_cnpj находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1199">The function Func_brazil_cnpj finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1200">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_brazil_cnpj;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1200">A keyword from Keyword_brazil_cnpj is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1201">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1201">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1202">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1202">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1203">функция Func_brazil_cnpj находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1203">The function Func_brazil_cnpj finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1204">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1204">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Brazil Legal Entity Number (CNPJ) -->
<Entity id="9b58b5cd-5e90-4df6-b34f-1ebcc88ceae4" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cnpj"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_brazil_cnpj"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cnpj"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1205">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1205">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_brazil_cnpj"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1206">Keyword_brazil_cnpj</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1206">Keyword_brazil_cnpj</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1207">CNPJ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1207">CNPJ</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1208">CNPJ/MF</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1208">CNPJ/MF</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1209">CNPJ – MF</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1209">CNPJ-MF</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1210">National Registry of Legal Entities</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1210">National Registry of Legal Entities</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1211">Taxpayers Registry</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1211">Taxpayers Registry</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1213">Legal entities</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1213">Legal entities</span></span>

## <a name="brazil-national-identification-card-rg"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1226">Национальная идентификационная карточка Бразилии (RG)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1226">Brazil national identification card (RG)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1227">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1227">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1228">Registro Geral (старый формат): девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1228">Registro Geral (old format): Nine digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1229">Registro de identidade (RIC) (новый формат): 11 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1229">Registro de Identidade (RIC) (new format): 11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1230">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1230">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1231">Registro Geral (старый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1231">Registro Geral (old format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1232">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1232">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1233">точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1233">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1234">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1234">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1235">точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1235">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1236">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1236">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1237">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1237">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1238">одна цифра, представляющая собой контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1238">one digit which is a check digit</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1239">Registro de identidade (RIC) (новый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1239">Registro de Identidade (RIC) (new format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1240">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1240">ten digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1241">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1241">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1242">одна цифра, представляющая собой контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1242">one digit which is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1243">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1243">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1244">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1244">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1245">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1245">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1246">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1246">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1247">функция Func_brazil_rg находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1247">The function Func_brazil_rg finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1248">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_brazil_rg;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1248">A keyword from Keyword_brazil_rg is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1249">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1249">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1250">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1250">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1251">функция Func_brazil_rg находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1251">The function Func_brazil_rg finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1252">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1252">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Brazil National ID Card (RG) -->
<Entity id="486de900-db70-41b3-a886-abdf25af119c" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_rg"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_brazil_rg"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_rg"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1253">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1253">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_brazil_rg"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1254">Keyword_brazil_rg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1254">Keyword_brazil_rg</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1255">Cédula de identidade</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1255">Cédula de identidade</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1256">identity card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1256">identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1257">national id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1257">national id</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1258">número de rregistro</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1258">número de rregistro</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1259">registro de Iidentidade</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1259">registro de Iidentidade</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1260">registro geral</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1260">registro geral</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1261">RG (ключевое слово с учетом регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1261">RG (this keyword is case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1262">RIC (ключевое слово с учетом регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1262">RIC (this keyword is case sensitive)</span></span> 


## <a name="bulgaria-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1263">Номер водительского удостоверения для Болгария</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1263">Bulgaria driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1264">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1264">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1265">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1265">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1266">девять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1266">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1267">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1267">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1268">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1268">nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1269">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1269">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1270">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1270">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1271">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1271">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1272">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1272">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1273">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1273">The regular expression  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1274">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1274">A keyword from  `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
             <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern> 
</Entity>    
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1275">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1275">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_bulgaria_eu_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1276">Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver "s_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1276">Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1283">drivers licence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1283">drivers licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1284">driver's license</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1284">driver's license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1285">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1285">driver's license number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1286">номер лицензии на драйвер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1286">driver's licence number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1287">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1287">driving license number</span></span>

## <a name="bulgaria-uniform-civil-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1293">Номер унифицированного гражданства Болгария</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1293">Bulgaria uniform civil number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1294">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1294">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1295">десять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1295">ten digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1296">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1296">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1297">десять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1297">ten digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1298">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (ГГММДД)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1298">six digits that correspond to the birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1299">две цифры, соответствующие порядку рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1299">two digits that correspond to the birth order</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1300">одна цифра, соответствующая Пол: четное число для пола и нечетная цифра для розетки</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1300">one digit that corresponds to gender: An even digit for male and an odd digit for female</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1301">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1301">one check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1302">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1302">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1303">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1303">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1304">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1304">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1305">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1305">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1306">Функция  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1306">The function  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1307">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1307">A keyword from  `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1308">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1308">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1309">Функция  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1309">The function  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Bulgaria Uniform Civil Number -->
      <Entity id="100d58b1-0a35-4fb1-aa89-e4a86fb53fcc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="bulgaria-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1354">Номер паспорта для Болгария</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1354">Bulgaria passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1355">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1355">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1356">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1356">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1357">девять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1357">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1358">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1358">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1359">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1359">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1360">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1360">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1361">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1361">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1362">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1362">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1363">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1363">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1364">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1364">The regular expression  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1365">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1365">A keyword from  `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1366">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1366">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1367">Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1367">Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1368">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1368">passport number</span></span>

## <a name="canada-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1372">Номер банковского счета для Канады</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1372">Canada bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1373">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1373">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1374">семь или двенадцать цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1374">seven or twelve digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1375">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1375">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1376">Номер банковского счета для Канады — семь или двенадцать цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1376">A Canada Bank Account Number is seven or twelve digits.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1377">Транзитный номер банковского счета в Канаде имеет указанный ниже формат.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1377">A Canada bank account transit number is:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1378">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1378">five digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1379">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1379">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1380">три цифры или</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1380">three digits OR</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1381">ноль "0"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1381">a zero "0"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1382">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1382">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1383">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1383">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1384">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1384">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1385">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1385">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1386">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1386">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1387">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1387">The regular expression Regex_canada_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1388">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_canada_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1388">A keyword from Keyword_canada_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1389">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_bank_account_transit_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1389">The regular expression Regex_canada_bank_account_transit_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1390">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1390">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1391">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1391">The regular expression Regex_canada_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1392">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_canada_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1392">A keyword from Keyword_canada_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="552e814c-cb50-4d94-bbaa-bb1d1ffb34de" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Regex_canada_bank_account_transit_number" />
   </Pattern>
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_bank_account_number" />
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1416">Номер водительского удостоверения для Канады</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1416">Canada driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1417">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1417">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1418">Зависит от провинции.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1418">Varies by province</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1419">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1419">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1420">Различные шаблоны, соответствующие провинциям Альберта, Британская Колумбия, Манитоба, Нью-Брансуик, Ньюфаундленд и Лабрадор, Новая Шотландия, Онтарио, Остров Принца Эдуарда, Квебек и Саскачеван.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1420">Various patterns covering Alberta, British Columbia, Manitoba, New Brunswick, Newfoundland/Labrador, Nova Scotia, Ontario, Prince Edward Island, Quebec, and Saskatchewan</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1421">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1421">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1422">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1422">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1423">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1423">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1424">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1424">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1425">функция Func_[province_name]_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1425">The function Func_[province_name]_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1426">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_[province_name]_drivers_license_name;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1426">A keyword from Keyword_[province_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1427">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_canada_drivers_license.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1427">A keyword from Keyword_canada_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Driver's License Number -->
    <Entity id="37186abb-8e48-4800-ad3c-e3d1610b3db0" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_alberta_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_alberta_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_british_columbia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_british_columbia_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_manitoba_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_manitoba_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_brunswick_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_new_brunswick_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_newfoundland_labrador_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_newfoundland_labrador_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_nova_scotia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_nova_scotia_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_ontario_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ontario_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_prince_edward_island_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_prince_edward_island_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_quebec_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_quebec_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_saskatchewan_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_saskatchewan_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-health-service-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1563">Номер службы здравоохранения для Канады</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1563">Canada health service number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1564">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1564">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1565">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1565">ten digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1566">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1566">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1567">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1567">ten digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1568">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1568">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1569">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1569">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1570">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1570">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1571">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1571">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1572">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_health_service_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1572">The regular expression Regex_canada_health_service_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1573">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_canada_health_service_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1573">A keyword from Keyword_canada_health_service_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Health Service Number -->
<Entity id="59c0bf39-7fab-482c-af25-00faa4384c94" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_health_service_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_health_service_number" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1574">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1574">Keywords</span></span>
