- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1576">personal health number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1576">personal health number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1577">patient information</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1577">patient information</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1578">health services</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1578">health services</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1579">speciality services</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1579">speciality services</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1580">automobile accident</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1580">automobile accident</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1581">patient hospital</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1581">patient hospital</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1582">псичиатрист</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1582">psychiatrist</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1583">workers compensation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1583">workers compensation</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1584">ограничен</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1584">disability</span></span>

      
## <a name="canada-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1585">Номер паспорта для Канады</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1585">Canada passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1586">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1586">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1587">две прописные буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1587">two uppercase letters followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1588">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1588">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1589">две прописные буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1589">two uppercase letters followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1590">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1590">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1591">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1591">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1592">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1592">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1593">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1593">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1594">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_passport_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1594">The regular expression Regex_canada_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1595">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_canada_passport_number или Keyword_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1595">A keyword from Keyword_canada_passport_number or Keyword_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml 
<!-- Canada Passport Number -->
<Entity id="14d0db8b-498a-43ed-9fca-f6097ae687eb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_passport_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-personal-health-identification-number-phin"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1625">Идентификационный номер персонального контроля работоспособности для Канады (PHIN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1625">Canada personal health identification number (PHIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1626">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1626">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1627">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1627">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1628">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1628">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1629">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1629">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1630">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1630">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1631">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1631">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1632">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1632">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1633">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1633">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1634">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_phin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1634">The regular expression Regex_canada_phin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1635">Найдены по крайней мере два ключевых слова от Keyword_canada_phin или Keyword_canada_provinces.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1635">At least two keywords from Keyword_canada_phin or Keyword_canada_provinces are found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada PHIN -->
<Entity id="722e12ac-c89a-4ec8-a1b7-fea3469f89db" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_phin" />
        <Any minMatches="2">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_phin" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_provinces" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-social-insurance-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1668">Номер социального страхования для Канады</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1668">Canada social insurance number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1669">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1669">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1670">девять цифр с необязательными дефисами или пробелами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1670">nine digits with optional hyphens or spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1671">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1671">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1672">Форматируемые</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1672">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1673">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1673">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1674">дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1674">a hyphen or space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1675">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1675">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1676">дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1676">a hyphen or space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1677">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1677">three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1678">Неформатированные: девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1678">Unformatted: nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1679">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1679">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1680">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1680">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1681">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1681">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1682">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1682">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1683">Функция Func_canadian_sin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1683">The function Func_canadian_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1684">Выполняются по меньшей мере два из таких условий:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1684">At least two of any combination of the following:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1685">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_sin;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1685">A keyword from Keyword_sin is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1686">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_sin_collaborative;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1686">A keyword from Keyword_sin_collaborative is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1687">функция Func_eu_date находит дату в правильном формате.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1687">The function Func_eu_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1688">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1688">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1689">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1689">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1690">функция Func_unformatted_canadian_sin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1690">The function Func_unformatted_canadian_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1691">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_sin;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1691">A keyword from Keyword_sin is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1692">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1692">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Social Insurance Number -->
<Entity id="a2f29c85-ecb8-4514-a610-364790c0773e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_canadian_sin" />
        <Any minMatches="2">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_sin" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_sin_collaborative" />
          <Match idRef="Func_eu_date" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_canadian_sin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_sin" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="chile-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1717">Номер идентификационной карточки Чили</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1717">Chile identity card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1718">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1718">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1719">семь и 8 цифр, а также разделители и контрольная цифра или буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1719">seven to eight digits plus delimiters a check digit or letter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1720">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1720">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1721">семь до восьми цифр, а также разделители:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1721">seven to eight digits plus delimiters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1722">одна – две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1722">one to two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1723">точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1723">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1724">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1724">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1725">точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1725">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1726">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1726">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1727">тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1727">a dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1728">одна цифра или буква (без учета регистра), которая является контрольной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1728">one digit or letter (not case sensitive) which is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1729">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1729">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1730">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1730">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1731">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1731">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1732">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1732">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1733">функция Func_chile_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1733">The function Func_chile_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1734">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_chile_id_card;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1734">A keyword from Keyword_chile_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1735">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1735">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1736">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1736">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1737">функция Func_chile_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1737">The function Func_chile_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1738">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1738">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Chile Identity Card Number -->
<Entity id="4e979794-49a0-407e-a0b9-2c536937b925" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_chile_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_chile_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_chile_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1739">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1739">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_chile_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1740">Keyword_chile_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1740">Keyword_chile_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1741">National Identification Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1741">National Identification Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1742">Identity card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1742">Identity card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1743">ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1743">ID</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1744">Процедура</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1744">Identification</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1745">Rol Único Nacional</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1745">Rol Único Nacional</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1746">ВЫПОЛНЯЕМ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1746">RUN</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1747">Rol Único Tributario</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1747">Rol Único Tributario</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1748">СНИЖАТЬСЯ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1748">RUT</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1749">Cédula de Identidad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1749">Cédula de Identidad</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1750">Número De Identificación Nacional</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1750">Número De Identificación Nacional</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1751">Tarjeta de identificación</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1751">Tarjeta de identificación</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1752">идентификаЦиóн</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1752">Identificación</span></span> 

   
## <a name="china-resident-identity-card-prc-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1753">Номер почтовых карточек для Китая (КНР)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1753">China resident identity card (PRC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1754">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1754">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1755">18 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1755">18 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1756">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1756">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1757">18 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1757">18 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1758">шесть цифр, которые являются кодом адреса</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1758">six digits which are an address code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1759">восемь цифр в формате ГГГГММДД, представляющие собой дату рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1759">eight digits in the form YYYYMMDD which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1760">три цифры, которые являются кодом заказа</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1760">three digits which are an order code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1761">одна цифра, представляющая собой контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1761">one digit which is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1762">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1762">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1763">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1763">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1764">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1764">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1765">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1765">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1766">функция Func_china_resident_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1766">The function Func_china_resident_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1767">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_china_resident_id;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1767">A keyword from Keyword_china_resident_id is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1768">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1768">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1769">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1769">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1770">функция Func_china_resident_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1770">The function Func_china_resident_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1771">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1771">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- China Resident Identity Card (PRC) Number -->
<Entity id="c92daa86-2d16-4871-901f-816b3f554fc1" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_china_resident_id"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_china_resident_id"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_china_resident_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1772">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1772">Keywords</span></span>

### <a name="keyword_china_resident_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1773">Keyword_china_resident_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1773">Keyword_china_resident_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1774">Resident Identity Card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1774">Resident Identity Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1775">NO7</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1775">PRC</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1776">National Identification Card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1776">National Identification Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1777">身份证</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1777">身份证</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1778">居民 身份证</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1778">居民 身份证</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1779">居民身份证</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1779">居民身份证</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1780">鉴定</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1780">鉴定</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1781">身分證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1781">身分證</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1782">居民 身份證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1782">居民 身份證</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1783">鑑定</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1783">鑑定</span></span> 

   
## <a name="credit-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1784">Номер кредитной карты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1784">Credit card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1785">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1785">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1786">14 – 16 цифр, которые можно форматировать или неформатированные (цццццццццццццццц) и которые должны пройти проверку Луна.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1786">14 to 16 digits which can be formatted or unformatted (dddddddddddddddd) and which must pass the Luhn test.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1787">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1787">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1788">Очень сложный и надежный шаблон, который определяет карты всех основных мировых стандартов, включая Visa, MasterCard, Discover Card, JCB, American Express, подарочные карты и карты Diners Club.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1788">Very complex and robust pattern that detects cards from all major brands worldwide, including Visa, MasterCard, Discover Card, JCB, American Express, gift cards, and diner cards.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1789">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1789">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1790">Да (рассчитывается по алгоритму Луна).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1790">Yes, the Luhn checksum</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1791">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1791">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1792">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1792">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1793">Функция Func_credit_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1793">The function Func_credit_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1794">Верно одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1794">One of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1795">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_cc_verification;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1795">A keyword from Keyword_cc_verification is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1796">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_cc_name;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1796">A keyword from Keyword_cc_name is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1797">функция Func_expiration_date находит дату в правильном формате.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1797">The function Func_expiration_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1798">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1798">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1799">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1799">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1800">функция Func_credit_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1800">The function Func_credit_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-1801">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-1801">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Credit Card Number -->
<Entity id="50842eb7-edc8-4019-85dd-5a5c1f2bb085" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_credit_card" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_cc_verification" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_cc_name" />
          <Match idRef="Func_expiration_date" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_credit_card" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2061">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Хорватия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2061">Croatia driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2062">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2062">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2063">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2063">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2064">восемь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2064">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2065">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2065">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2066">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2066">eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2067">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2067">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2068">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2068">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2069">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2069">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2070">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2070">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2071">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2071">The regular expression  `Regex_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2072">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2072">A keyword from  `Keywords_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2088">Номер идентификационной карточки (Хорватия)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2088">Croatia identity card number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2089">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в тип конфиденциальной информации страны ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2089">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2090">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2090">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2091">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2091">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2092">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2092">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2093">девять последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2093">nine consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2094">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2094">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2095">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2095">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2096">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2096">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2097">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2097">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2098">функция Func_croatia_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2098">The function Func_croatia_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml

  </Pattern>
```

## <a name="croatia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2130">Номер паспорта для выхорватия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2130">Croatia passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2131">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2131">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2132">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2132">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2133">девять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2133">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2134">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2134">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2135">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2135">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2136">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2136">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2137">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2137">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2138">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2138">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2139">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2139">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2140">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2140">The regular expression  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2141">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2141">A keyword from  `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2142">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2142">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2143">Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2143">Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2144">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2144">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2145">номер паспорта для хорватского языка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2145">croatian passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2146">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2146">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2147">Брож путовнице</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2147">broj putovnice</span></span>

   
## <a name="croatia-personal-identification-oib-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2148">Номер личного кода (OIB), Хорватия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2148">Croatia personal identification (OIB) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2149">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2149">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2150">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2150">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2151">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2151">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2152">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2152">11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2153">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2153">ten digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2154">Последняя цифра — контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2154">final digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2155">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2155">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2156">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2156">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2157">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2157">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2158">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2158">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2159">функция Func_croatia_oib_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2159">The function Func_croatia_oib_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2160">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2160">A keyword from Keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2161">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2161">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2162">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2162">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2163">функция Func_croatia_oib_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2163">The function Func_croatia_oib_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2164">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2164">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Croatia Personal Identification (OIB) Number -->
      <Entity id="31983b6d-db95-4eb2-a630-b44bd091968d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_oib_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_oib_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-social-security-number-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2195">Хорватия номер социального страхования или эквивалентная идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2195">Croatia social security number or equivalent identification</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2196">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в номере социального страхования ЕС или эквивалентного идентификатора.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2196">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2197">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2197">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2198">11 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2198">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2199">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2199">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2200">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2200">11 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2201">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2201">ten digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2202">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2202">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2203">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2203">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2204">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2204">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2205">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2205">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2206">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2206">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2207">Функция  `Func_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2207">The function  `Func_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2208">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2208">A keyword from  `Keywords_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2209">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2209">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2210">Функция  `Func_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2210">The function  `Func_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU SSN or Equivalent Number -->
<Entity id="d24e32a4-c0bb-4ba8-899d-6303b95742d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern> 
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>      
</Entity>
```

## <a name="cyprus-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2227">Номер лицензии на драйверы Кипр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2227">Cyprus drivers license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2228">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2228">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2229">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2229">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2230">12 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2230">12 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2231">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2231">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2232">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2232">12 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2233">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2233">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2234">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2234">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2235">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2235">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2236">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2236">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2237">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2237">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2238">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2238">A keyword from  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="cyprus-identity-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2253">Идентификационная карточка Кипр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2253">Cyprus identity card</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2254">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2254">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2255">десять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2255">ten digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2256">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2256">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2257">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2257">ten digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2258">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2258">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2259">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2259">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2260">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2260">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2261">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2261">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2262">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2262">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2263">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2263">A keyword from  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml 
      <!-- Cyprus Identity Card -->
      <Entity id="3ba8afe5-7a6c-4929-8247-0001b6878438" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2264">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2264">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2267">Номер идентификационной карточки</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2267">identity card number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2270">личный идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2270">personal id number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2271">ταυτοτητασ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2271">ταυτοτητασ</span></span>


## <a name="cyprus-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2272">Номер паспорта для Кипр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2272">Cyprus passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2273">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2273">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2274">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2274">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2275">одна буква, за которой следуют 6-8 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2275">one letter followed by 6-8 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2276">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2276">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2277">одна буква, за которой следуют шесть и восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2277">one letter followed by six to eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2278">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2278">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2279">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2279">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2280">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2280">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2281">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2281">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2282">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2282">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2283">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2283">A keyword from  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2284">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2284">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2285">Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2285">Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2286">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2286">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2287">номер паспорта для Кипр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2287">cyprus passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2288">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2288">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2289">αριθμό διαβατηρίου</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2289">αριθμό διαβατηρίου</span></span>


## <a name="cyprus-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2290">Идентификационный номер налогоплательщика (Кипр)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2290">Cyprus tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2291">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2291">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2292">восемь цифр и одна буква в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2292">eight digits and one letter in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2293">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2293">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2294">восемь цифр и одна буква:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2294">eight digits and one letter:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2295">"0" или "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2295">a "0" or "9"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2296">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2296">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2297">одна буква (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2297">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2298">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2298">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2299">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2299">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2300">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2300">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2301">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2301">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2302">Функция  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2302">The function  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2303">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2303">A keyword from  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2304">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2304">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2305">Функция  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2305">The function  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Cyprus Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="40e64bd9-55f3-4a09-9bd6-1db18dced9dd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="czech-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2333">Номер водительского удостоверения для чешского языка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2333">Czech driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2334">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2334">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2335">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2335">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2336">две буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2336">two letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2337">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2337">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2338">восемь букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2338">eight letters and digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2339">две буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2339">two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2340">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2340">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2341">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2341">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2342">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2342">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2343">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2343">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2344">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2344">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2345">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2345">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2346">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2346">The regular expression  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2347">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2347">A keyword from  `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>

```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2348">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2348">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_czech_republic_eu_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2349">Keywords_czech_republic_eu_driver "s_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2349">Keywords_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2353">Лицензия на драйвер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2353">driver licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2354">Drivers лик.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2354">drivers lic.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2356">drivers licence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2356">drivers licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2357">driver's license</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2357">driver's license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2358">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2358">driver's license number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2359">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2359">driver's license number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2360">номер лицензии на драйвер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2360">driver's licence number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2361">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2361">driving license number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2362">длно #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2362">dlno#</span></span>

## <a name="czech-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2364">Номер паспорта для чешского языка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2364">Czech passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2365">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2365">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2366">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2366">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2367">восемь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2367">eight digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2368">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2368">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2369">восемь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2369">eight digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2370">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2370">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2371">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2371">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2372">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2372">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2373">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2373">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2374">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2374">The regular expression  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2375">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2375">A keyword from  `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2376">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2376">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2377">Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2377">Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2378">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2378">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2379">номер паспорта для чешского языка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2379">czech passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2380">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2380">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2381">цестовнí PAS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2381">cestovní pas</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2382">соответствующий</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2382">pas</span></span>


## <a name="czech-personal-identity-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2383">Номер личного удостоверения для чешского языка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2383">Czech personal identity number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2384">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2384">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2385">девять цифр с необязательной косой чертой (старый формат), десять цифрами с необязательной косой чертой (новый формат)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2385">nine digits with optional forward slash (old format) ten digits with optional forward slash (new format)</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2386">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2386">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2387">девять цифр (старый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2387">nine digits (old format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2388">шесть цифр, представляющих дату рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2388">six digits that represent date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2389">Необязательная косая черта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2389">an optional forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2390">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2390">three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2391">десять цифр (новый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2391">ten digits (new format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2392">шесть цифр, представляющих дату рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2392">six digits that represent date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2393">Необязательная косая черта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2393">an optional forward slash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2394">четыре цифры, где последняя цифра является контрольной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2394">four digits where last digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2395">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2395">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2396">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2396">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2397">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2397">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2398">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2398">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2399">функция Func_czech_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2399">The function Func_czech_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2400">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_czech_id_card;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2400">A keyword from Keyword_czech_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2401">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2401">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2402">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2402">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2403">Функция Func_czech_id_card_new_format находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2403">The function Func_czech_id_card_new_format finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-2404">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-2404">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Czech Personal Identity Number -->
      <!-- Czech Personal Identity Number -->
      <Entity id="60c0725a-4eb6-455b-9dda-05d8a7396497" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_czech_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_czech_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Version minEngineVersion="15.20.3000.000">
          <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
            <IdMatch idRef="Func_czech_id_card_new_format" />
          </Pattern>
        </Version>
      </Entity>
```
