## <a name="france-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3485">Номер паспорта для Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3485">France passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3486">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3486">This sensitive information type entity is available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3487">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3487">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3488">девять цифр и букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3488">nine digits and letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3489">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3489">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3490">девять цифр и букв:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3490">nine digits and letters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3491">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3491">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3492">две буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3492">two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3493">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3493">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3494">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3494">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3495">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3495">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3496">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3496">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3497">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3497">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3498">функция Func_fr_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3498">The function Func_fr_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3499">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3499">A keyword from Keyword_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- France Passport Number -->
<Entity id="3008b884-8c8c-4cd8-a289-99f34fc7ff5d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_fr_passport" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3500">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3500">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3509">パスポート</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3509">パスポート</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3510">パスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3510">パスポート番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3511">パスポートのнум</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3511">パスポートのNum</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3512">パスポート＃</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3512">パスポート ＃</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3513">Numéro de passeport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3513">Numéro de passeport</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3517">пассепорт #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3517">Passeport#</span></span>

## <a name="france-social-security-number-insee-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3520">Номер социального страхования для Франции (INSEE) или эквивалентная идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3520">France social security number (INSEE) or equivalent identification</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3521">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в номер социального страхования ЕС и эквивалентный тип конфиденциальной информации и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3521">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Social Security Number and Equivalent ID sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3522">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3522">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3523">15 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3523">15 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3524">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3524">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3525">Должен соответствовать одному из двух шаблонов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3525">Must match one of two patterns:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3526">13 цифр, за которыми следует пробел, за которым следуют две цифры.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3526">13 digits followed by a space followed by two digits</span></span><br/>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3527">или</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3527">or</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3528">15 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3528">15 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3529">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3529">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3530">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3530">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3531">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3531">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3532">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 95 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3532">A DLP policy is 95% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3533">Функция Func_french_insee или Func_fr_insee находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3533">The function Func_french_insee or Func_fr_insee finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3534">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_fr_insee;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3534">A keyword from Keyword_fr_insee is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3535">контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3535">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3536">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3536">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3537">Функция Func_french_insee или Func_fr_insee находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3537">The function Func_french_insee or Func_fr_insee finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3538">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_fr_insee не находится;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3538">No keyword from Keyword_fr_insee is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3539">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3539">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- France INSEE -->
<Entity id="71f62b97-efe0-4aa1-aa49-e14de253619d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="95">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_french_insee" />
        <Match idRef="Func_fr_insee" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_fr_insee" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_french_insee" />
        <Match idRef="Func_fr_insee" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_fr_insee" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3551">numero d'identite</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3551">numero d'identite</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3553">Нет.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3553">no.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3554">д'идентите</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3554">d'identite</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3555">social security number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3555">social security number</span></span>

## <a name="france-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3565">Налоговый идентификационный номер для Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3565">France tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3566">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3566">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3567">13 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3567">13 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3568">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3568">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3569">13 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3569">13 digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3570">Одна цифра, которая должна быть равна 0, 1, 2 или 3</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3570">One digit that must be 0, 1, 2, or 3</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3571">1 цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3571">1 digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3572">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3572">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3573">2 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3573">2 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3574">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3574">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3575">3 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3575">3 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3576">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3576">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3577">3 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3577">3 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3578">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3578">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3579">3 контрольные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3579">3 check digits</span></span> 

  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3580">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3580">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3581">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3581">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3582">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3582">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3583">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3583">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3584">Функция  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3584">The function  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3585">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3585">A keyword from  `Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3586">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3586">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3587">Функция  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3587">The function  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- France Tax Identification Number (numéro SPI.) -->
      <Entity id="ed59e77e-171d-442c-9ec1-88e2ebcb5b0a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3588">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3588">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3589">Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3589">Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3590">нумéро д'идентификатион Фин.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3590">numéro d'identification fiscale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3591">tax id
</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3591">tax id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3592">Налоговый идентификатор</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3592">tax identification no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3593">идентификационный номер налога</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3593">tax identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3594">налог без #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3594">tax no#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3595">налог без</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3595">tax no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3596">Налоговый номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3596">tax number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3597">Регистрационный номер налогоплательщика</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3597">tax registration number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3598">такси #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3598">taxid#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3599">таксидно #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3599">taxidno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3600">таксиднумбер #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3600">taxidnumber#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3601">таксно #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3601">taxno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3602">такснумбер #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3602">taxnumber#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3603">такснумбер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3603">taxnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3604">Идентификатор Tin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3604">tin id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3605">номер Tin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3605">tin no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3606">ИНН #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3606">tin#</span></span>


## <a name="france-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3607">Значение налогового номера, добавленного в Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3607">France value added tax number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3608">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3608">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3609">13-буквенно-буквенно-цифровой шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3609">13 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3610">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3610">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3611">13 символов буквенно-цифрового шаблона:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3611">13 character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3612">две буквы — FR (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3612">two letters  - FR (case insensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3613">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3613">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3614">две буквы или цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3614">two letters or digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3615">необязательный пробел, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3615">an optional space, dot, hyphen or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3616">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3616">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3617">необязательный пробел, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3617">an optional space, dot, hyphen or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3618">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3618">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3619">необязательный пробел, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3619">an optional space, dot, hyphen or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3620">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3620">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3621">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3621">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3622">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3622">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3623">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3623">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3624">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3624">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3625">Функция Func_france_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3625">The function Func_france_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3626">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3626">A keyword from Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3627">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3627">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3628">Функция Func_france_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3628">The function Func_france_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- France Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="949121e6-ad9f-4379-8731-710342baea78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3629">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3629">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_france_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3630">Keyword_France_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3630">Keyword_France_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3631">номер НДС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3631">vat number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3632">НДС No</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3632">vat no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3633">процент #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3633">vat#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3634">налог на добавленную стоимость</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3634">value added tax</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3635">Siren идентификация No нумéро д'идентификатион таксе Сур валеур ажаутéе</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3635">siren identification no numéro d'identification taxe sur valeur ajoutée</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3636">таксе валеур ажаутéе</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3636">taxe valeur ajoutée</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3637">таксе Сур Ла валеур ажаутéе</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3637">taxe sur la valeur ajoutée</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3638">n ° тва</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3638">n° tva</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3639">нумéро de тва</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3639">numéro de tva</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3640">нумéро д'идентификатион Siren</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3640">numéro d'identification siren</span></span>


## <a name="germany-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3641">Номер водительского удостоверения для Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3641">Germany driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3642">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в тип конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3642">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3643">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3643">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3644">сочетание 11 цифр и букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3644">combination of 11 digits and letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3645">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3645">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3646">11 цифр и букв (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3646">11 digits and letters (not case sensitive):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3647">цифра или буква;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3647">a digit or letter</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3648">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3648">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3649">шесть цифр или букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3649">six digits or letters</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3650">цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3650">a digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3651">цифра или буква;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3651">a digit or letter</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3652">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3652">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3653">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3653">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3654">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3654">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3655">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3655">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3656">Функция Func_german_drivers_license находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3656">The function Func_german_drivers_license finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3657">Верно по меньшей мере одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3657">At least one of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3658">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_german_drivers_license_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3658">A keyword from Keyword_german_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3659">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_german_drivers_license_collaborative;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3659">A keyword from Keyword_german_drivers_license_collaborative is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3660">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_german_drivers_license.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3660">A keyword from Keyword_german_drivers_license is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3661">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3661">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Germany Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="91da9335-1edb-45b7-a95f-5fe41a16c63c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_drivers_license" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_drivers_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_drivers_license_collaborative" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_drivers_license" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="germany-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3754">Номер идентификационной карточки для Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3754">Germany identity card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3755">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3755">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3756">с 1 ноября 2010: девять букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3756">since 1 November 2010: Nine letters and digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3757">от 1 апреля 1987 до 31 октября 2010:10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3757">from 1 April 1987 until 31 October 2010: 10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3758">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3758">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3759">с 1 ноября 2010:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3759">since 1 November 2010:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3760">одна буква (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3760">one letter (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3761">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3761">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3762">от 1 апреля 1987 до 31 октября 2010:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3762">from 1 April 1987 until 31 October 2010:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3763">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3763">ten digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3764">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3764">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3765">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3765">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3766">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3766">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3767">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3767">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3768">регулярное выражение Regex_germany_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3768">The regular expression Regex_germany_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3769">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_germany_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3769">A keyword from Keyword_germany_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Germany Identity Card Number -->
<Entity id="e577372f-c42e-47a0-9d85-bebed1c237d4" recommendedConfidence="65" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_germany_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_germany_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3770">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3770">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_germany_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3771">Keyword_germany_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3771">Keyword_germany_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3772">аусвеис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3772">ausweis</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3773">гпид</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3773">gpid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3774">процедура</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3774">identification</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3775">идентификатион</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3775">identifikation</span></span>

## <a name="germany-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3785">Номер паспорта для Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3785">Germany passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3786">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в тип конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3786">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3787">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3787">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3788">десять цифр или букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3788">ten digits or letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3789">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3789">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3790">Шаблон должен включать в себя все указанные ниже элементы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3790">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3791">Первый символ — цифра или буква из этого набора (C, F, G, H, J, K)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3791">first character is a digit or a letter from this set (C, F, G, H, J, K)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3792">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3792">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3793">пять цифр или букв из этого набора (C,-H, J-N, P, R, T, V-Z)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3793">five digits or letters from this set (C, -H, J-N, P, R, T, V-Z)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3794">цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3794">a digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3795">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3795">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3796">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3796">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3797">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3797">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3798">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3798">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3799">функция Func_german_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3799">The function Func_german_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3800">находится любое ключевое слово из пяти соответствующих списков;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3800">A keyword from any of the five keyword lists is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3801">контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3801">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3802">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3802">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3803">функция Func_german_passport_data находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3803">The function Func_german_passport_data finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3804">находится любое ключевое слово из пяти соответствующих списков;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3804">A keyword from any of the five keyword lists is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3805">контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3805">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Germany Passport Number -->
<Entity id="2e3da144-d42b-47ed-b123-fbf78604e52c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_passport" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport_collaborative" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport1" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport2" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_passport_data" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport_collaborative" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport1" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport2" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3810">реисепасснуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3810">reisepassnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3811">службу</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3811">passport</span></span>

## <a name="germany-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3823">Идентификационный номер налогоплательщика (Германия)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3823">Germany tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3824">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3824">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3825">11 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3825">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3826">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3826">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3827">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3827">11 digits :</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3828">Две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3828">Two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3829">Необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3829">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3830">Три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3830">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3831">Необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3831">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3832">Три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3832">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3833">Необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3833">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3834">Две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3834">Two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3835">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3835">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3836">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3836">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3837">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3837">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3838">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3838">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3839">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3839">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3840">Функция  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3840">The function  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3841">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3841">A keyword from  `Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3842">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3842">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3843">Функция  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3843">The function  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Germany Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="43316a89-9880-40cf-b980-04bc7eefcec5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3844">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3844">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3853">налог без #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3853">tax no#</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3855">Налоговый номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3855">tax number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3856">Регистрационный номер налогоплательщика</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3856">tax registration number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3857">такси #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3857">taxid#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3858">таксидно #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3858">taxidno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3859">таксиднумбер #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3859">taxidnumber#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3860">таксно #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3860">taxno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3861">такснумбер #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3861">taxnumber#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3862">такснумбер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3862">taxnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3863">Идентификатор Tin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3863">tin id</span></span>

## <a name="germany-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3869">Значение налогового номера добавленного в Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3869">Germany value added tax number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3870">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3870">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3871">11 буквенно-цифрового шаблона</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3871">11 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3872">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3872">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3873">11-буквенно-цифровой буквенно-значный шаблон:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3873">11-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3874">буква D или d</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3874">a letter D or d</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3875">буква E или e</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3875">a letter E or e</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3876">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3876">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3877">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3877">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3878">необязательный пробел или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3878">an optional space or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3879">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3879">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3880">необязательный пробел или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3880">an optional space or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3881">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3881">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3882">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3882">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3883">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3883">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3884">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3884">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3885">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3885">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3886">Функция Func_germany_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3886">The function Func_germany_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3887">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3887">A keyword from Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3888">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3888">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3889">Функция Func_germany_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3889">The function Func_germany_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Germany Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="db177eb2-8811-4842-bffc-128c14aa219f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3890">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3890">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_germany_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3891">Keyword_germany_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3891">Keyword_germany_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3892">номер НДС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3892">vat number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3893">НДС No</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3893">vat no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3894">процент #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3894">vat#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3895">НДС # мехрвертстеуер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3895">vat#  mehrwertsteuer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3896">мвст</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3896">mwst</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3897">мехрвертстеуер идентификатионснуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3897">mehrwertsteuer identifikationsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3898">мехрвертстеуер нуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3898">mehrwertsteuer nummer</span></span>


## <a name="greece-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3899">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Греция</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3899">Greece driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3900">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в тип конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3900">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3901">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3901">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3902">девять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3902">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3903">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3903">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3904">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3904">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3905">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3905">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3906">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3906">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3907">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3907">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3908">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3908">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3909">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3909">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3910">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3910">A keyword from  `Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3911">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3911">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_greece_eu_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3912">Keywords_greece_eu_driver "s_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3912">Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3913">Файл #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3913">dlL#</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3915">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3915">driver license number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3916">Лицензия на драйвер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3916">driver licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3917">Drivers лик.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3917">drivers lic.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3918">drivers license</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3918">drivers license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3919">drivers licence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3919">drivers licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3920">driver's license</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3920">driver's license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3921">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3921">driver's license number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3922">номер лицензии на драйвер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3922">driver's licence number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3923">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3923">driving license number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3924">длно #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3924">dlno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3925">δεια οδήγησης</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3925">δεια οδήγησης</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3926">Адеиа одигисис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3926">Adeia odigisis</span></span>


## <a name="greece-national-id-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3927">Национальный идентификационный номер карты (Греция)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3927">Greece national ID card</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3928">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3928">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3929">Сочетание 7–8 букв и чисел, а также тире.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3929">Combination of 7-8 letters and numbers plus a dash</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3930">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3930">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3931">Семь букв и чисел (старый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3931">Seven letters and numbers (old format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3932">одна буква (любая буква греческого алфавита);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3932">One letter (any letter of the Greek alphabet)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3933">тире;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3933">A dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3934">шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3934">Six digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3935">Восемь букв и чисел (новый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3935">Eight letters and numbers (new format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3936">две буквы, которые в прописном виде есть как в греческом, так и латинском алфавите (ABEZHIKMNOPTYX);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3936">Two letters whose uppercase character occurs in both the Greek and Latin alphabets (ABEZHIKMNOPTYX)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3937">тире;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3937">A dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3938">шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3938">Six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3939">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3939">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3940">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3940">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3941">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3941">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3942">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3942">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3943">регулярное выражение Regex_greece_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3943">The regular expression Regex_greece_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3944">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_greece_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3944">A keyword from Keyword_greece_id_card is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3945">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3945">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3946">регулярное выражение Regex_greece_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3946">The regular expression Regex_greece_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Greece National ID Card -->
      <Entity id="82568215-1da1-46d3-874a-d2294d81b5ac" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_greece_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3947">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3947">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_greece_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3948">Keyword_greece_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3948">Keyword_greece_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3949">Греческий идентификатор</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3949">greek id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3950">Греческая национальная идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3950">greek national id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3951">Греческая личная идентификационная карточка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3951">greek personal id card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3952">код греческой политики</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3952">greek police id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3953">идентификационная карточка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3953">identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3954">таутотита</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3954">tautotita</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3955">ταυτότητα</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3955">ταυτότητα</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3956">ταυτότητας</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3956">ταυτότητας</span></span>


## <a name="greece-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3957">Номер паспорта для Греция</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3957">Greece passport number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3958">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3958">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3959">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3959">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3960">Две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3960">Two letters followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3961">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3961">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3962">Две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3962">Two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3963">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3963">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3964">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3964">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3965">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3965">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3966">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3966">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3967">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3967">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3968">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3968">A keyword from  `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="greece-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3975">Идентификационный номер налога в Греция</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3975">Greece tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3976">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3976">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3977">Девять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3977">Nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3978">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3978">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3979">Девять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3979">Nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3980">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3980">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3981">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3981">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3982">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3982">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3983">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3983">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3984">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3984">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-3985">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-3985">A keyword from  `Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Greek Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="15a54a5a-53d4-4080-ad43-a2a4fe1d3bf7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="hong-kong-identity-card-hkid-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4014">Номер идентификационной карточки Гонконг (HKID)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4014">Hong Kong identity card (HKID) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4015">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4015">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4016">Сочетание 8–9 букв и чисел, а также необязательные скобки вокруг последнего символа.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4016">Combination of 8-9 letters and numbers plus optional parentheses around the final character</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4017">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4017">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4018">Сочетание 8–9 букв:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4018">Combination of 8-9 letters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4019">1–2 буквы (без учета регистра);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4019">1-2 letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4020">шесть цифр; </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4020">Six digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4021">последний символ (любая цифра или буква "A") является проверочной цифрой и заключен в скобки (необязательно).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4021">The final character (any digit or the letter A), which is the check digit and is optionally enclosed in parentheses.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4022">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4022">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4023">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4023">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4024">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4024">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4025">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4025">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4026">функция Func_hong_kong_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4026">The function Func_hong_kong_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4027">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_hong_kong_id_card;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4027">A keyword from Keyword_hong_kong_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4028">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4028">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4029">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4029">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4030">функция Func_hong_kong_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4030">The function Func_hong_kong_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4031">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4031">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Hong Kong Identity Card (HKID) number -->
<Entity id="e63c28a7-ad29-4c17-a41a-3d2a0b70fd9c" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_hong_kong_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_hong_kong_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_hong_kong_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4065">香港特別行政區永久性居民身分證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4065">香港特別行政區永久性居民身分證</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4066">香港特別行政區永久性居民身分証</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4066">香港特別行政區永久性居民身分証</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4067">香港特別行政區非永久性居民身份證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4067">香港特別行政區非永久性居民身份證</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4068">香港特別行政區非永久性居民身份証</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4068">香港特別行政區非永久性居民身份証</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4069">香港特別行政區非永久性居民身分證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4069">香港特別行政區非永久性居民身分證</span></span>

## <a name="hungary-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4071">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Венгрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4071">Hungary driver's license number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4072">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4072">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4073">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4073">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4074">Две буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4074">Two letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4075">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4075">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4076">Две буквы и шесть цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4076">Two letters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4077">Две буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4077">Two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4078">шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4078">Six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4079">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4079">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4080">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4080">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4081">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4081">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4082">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4082">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4083">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4083">The regular expression  `Regex_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4084">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4084">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4085">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4085">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4089">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4089">driver license number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4090">Лицензия на драйвер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4090">driver licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4091">Drivers лик.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4091">drivers lic.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4092">drivers license</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4092">drivers license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4093">drivers licence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4093">drivers licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4094">driver's license</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4094">driver's license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4095">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4095">driver's license number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4096">номер лицензии на драйвер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4096">driver's licence number</span></span>
