## <a name="hungary-personal-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4100">Венгрия персональный идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4100">Hungary personal identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4101">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4101">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4102">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4102">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4103">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4103">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4104">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4104">11 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4105">Одна цифра, соответствующая пол (1-м-штекер, 2-гнездо, другие номера также могут иметь гражданские телефоны перед 1900 или гражданами с удвоенной гражданией)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4105">One digit that corresponds to gender (1-male, 2-female, other numbers are also possible for citizens born before 1900 or citizens with double citizenship)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4106">Шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (ГГММДД)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4106">Six digits that correspond to birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4107">Три цифры, соответствующие серийному номеру.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4107">Three digits that correspond to a serial number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4108">Одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4108">One check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4109">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4109">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4110">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4110">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4111">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4111">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4112">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4112">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4113">Функция  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4113">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4114">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4114">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4115">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4115">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4116">Функция  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4116">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Hungary Personal Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="7b5cc218-7046-47d9-80c9-f325b50896ca" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4117">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4117">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4118">Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4118">Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4119">идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4119">id number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4120">identification number
</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4120">identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4121">СЗ IG</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4121">sz ig</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4122">СЗ.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4122">sz.</span></span><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4123">IG.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4123"> ig.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4124">СЗ. IG.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4124">sz.ig.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4125">сземéлязоносíтó игазолвáни</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4125">személyazonosító igazolvány</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4126">сземéли игазолвáни</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4126">személyi igazolvány</span></span>


## <a name="hungary-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4127">Номер паспорта для Венгрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4127">Hungary passport number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4128">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4128">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4129">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4129">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4130">Две буквы, за которыми следуют шесть или семь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4130">Two letters followed by six or seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4131">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4131">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4132">Две буквы, за которыми следуют шесть или семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4132">Two letters followed by six or seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4133">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4133">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4134">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4134">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4135">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4135">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4136">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4136">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4137">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4137">The regular expression  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4138">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4138">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4139">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4139">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4140">Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4140">Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4141">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4141">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4142">Венгерский номер паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4142">hungarian passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4143">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4143">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4144">úтлевéл сзáма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4144">útlevél száma</span></span>


## <a name="hungary-social-security-number-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4145">Венгерский номер социального страхования или идентификация эквивалентных прав</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4145">Hungary social security number or equivalent identification</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4146">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в номере социального страхования ЕС или эквивалентного идентификатора.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4146">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4147">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4147">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4148">Девять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4148">Nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4149">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4149">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4150">Девять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4150">Nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4151">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4151">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4152">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4152">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4153">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4153">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4154">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4154">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4155">Функция  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4155">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4156">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4156">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4157">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4157">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4158">Функция  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4158">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU SSN or Equivalent Number -->
<Entity id="d24e32a4-c0bb-4ba8-899d-6303b95742d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern> 
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>      
</Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4178">Идентификационный номер венгерского налога</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4178">Hungary tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4179">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4179">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4180">Десять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4180">Ten digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4181">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4181">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4182">Десять цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4182">Ten digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4183">Одна цифра, которая должна быть "8"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4183">One digit that must be "8"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4184">восемь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4184">Eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4185">Одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4185">One check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4186">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4186">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4187">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4187">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4188">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4188">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4189">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4189">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4190">Функция  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4190">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4191">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4191">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4192">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4192">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4193">Функция  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4193">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Hungary Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="ede42eb4-59d9-49eb-9603-d7853fbda91d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4219">Венгерский номер добавленного значения налога</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4219">Hungary value added tax number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4220">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4220">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4221">10-буквенно-буквенно-цифровой шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4221">10 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4222">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4222">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4223">10 буквенно-цифровых буквенных символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4223">10 character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4224">2 буквы — HU или HU</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4224">2 letters - HU or hu</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4225">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4225">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4226">8 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4226">8 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4227">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4227">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4228">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4228">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4229">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4229">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4230">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4230">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4231">Функция Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4231">The function Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4232">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_hungarian_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4232">A keyword from Keywords_hungarian_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4233">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4233">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4234">Функция Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4234">The function Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Hungarian Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="976349a0-683b-477a-90f8-ff0a220d5592" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungarian_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_hungary_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4236">Keyword_Hungary_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4236">Keyword_Hungary_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4247">áфа сзáм</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4247">áfa szám</span></span>


## <a name="india-permanent-account-number-pan"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4248">Номер постоянного счета Индии (PAN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4248">India permanent account number (PAN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4249">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4249">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4250">10 букв или цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4250">10 letters or digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4251">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4251">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4252">10 букв или цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4252">10 letters or digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4253">пять букв (без учета регистра);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4253">Five letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4254">четыре цифры;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4254">Four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4255">буква, которая является алфавитным проверочным символом.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4255">A letter which is an alphabetic check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4256">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4256">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4257">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4257">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4258">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4258">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4259">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4259">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4260">регулярное выражение Regex_india_permanent_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4260">The regular expression Regex_india_permanent_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4261">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_india_permanent_account_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4261">A keyword from Keyword_india_permanent_account_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4262">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4262">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- India Permanent Account Number -->
<Entity id="2602bfee-9bb0-47a5-a7a6-2bf3053e2804" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_india_permanent_account_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_india_permanent_account_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4263">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4263">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_india_permanent_account_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4264">Keyword_india_permanent_account_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4264">Keyword_india_permanent_account_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4265">Permanent Account Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4265">Permanent Account Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4266">ПАНОРАМИРОВАНИЕ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4266">PAN</span></span> 
   
## <a name="india-unique-identification-aadhaar-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4267">Уникальный идентификационный номер (Aadhaar) Индии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4267">India unique identification (Aadhaar) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4268">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4268">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4269">12 цифр, содержащих необязательные пробелы или тире.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4269">12 digits containing optional spaces or dashes</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4270">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4270">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4271">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4271">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4272">четыре цифры;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4272">Four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4273">необязательный пробел или тире;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4273">An optional space or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4274">четыре цифры;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4274">Four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4275">необязательный пробел или тире;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4275">An optional space or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4276">последняя цифра — проверочная.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4276">The final digit which is the check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4277">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4277">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4278">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4278">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4279">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4279">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4280">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4280">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4281">функция Func_india_aadhaar находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4281">The function Func_india_aadhaar finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4282">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_india_aadhar;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4282">A keyword from Keyword_india_aadhar is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4283">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4283">The checksum passes.</span></span>
- 
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4284">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4284">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4285">функция Func_india_aadhaar находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4285">The function Func_india_aadhaar finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4286">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4286">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- India Unique Identification (Aadhaar) number -->
<Entity id="1ca46b29-76f5-4f46-9383-cfa15e91048f" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_india_aadhaar"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_india_aadhar"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_india_aadhaar"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4287">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4287">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_india_aadhar"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4288">Keyword_india_aadhar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4288">Keyword_india_aadhar</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4289">аадхар</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4289">Aadhar</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4290">Aadhaar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4290">Aadhaar</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4291">UID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4291">UID</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4292">आधार</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4292">आधार</span></span>
   
## <a name="indonesia-identity-card-ktp-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4293">Номер идентификационной карточки Индонезия (KTP)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4293">Indonesia identity card (KTP) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4294">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4294">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4295">16 цифр, содержащих необязательные точки.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4295">16 digits containing optional periods</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4296">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4296">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4297">16 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4297">16 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4298">две цифры (код провинции);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4298">Two-digit province code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4299">точка (необязательно);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4299">A period (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4300">две цифры (код округа или города);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4300">Two-digit regency or city code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4301">две цифры (код района);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4301">Two-digit subdistrict code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4302">точка (необязательно);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4302">A period (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4303">шесть цифр в формате ДДММГГ (дата рождения);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4303">Six digits in the format DDMMYY which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4304">точка (необязательно);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4304">A period (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4305">четыре цифры.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4305">Four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4306">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4306">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4307">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4307">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4308">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4308">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4309">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4309">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4310">регулярное выражение Regex_indonesia_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4310">The regular expression Regex_indonesia_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4311">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_indonesia_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4311">A keyword from Keyword_indonesia_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Indonesia Identity Card (KTP) Number -->
<Entity id="da68fdb0-f383-4981-8c86-82689d3b7d55" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_indonesia_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_indonesia_id_card"/>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4312">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4312">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_indonesia_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4313">Keyword_indonesia_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4313">Keyword_indonesia_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4314">KTP</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4314">KTP</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4315">Kartu Tanda Penduduk</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4315">Kartu Tanda Penduduk</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4316">Nomor Induk Kependudukan</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4316">Nomor Induk Kependudukan</span></span> 
   
## <a name="international-banking-account-number-iban"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4317">Международный номер банковского счета (IBAN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4317">International banking account number (IBAN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4318">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4318">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4319">Код страны (две буквы), а также проверочные цифры (две) и номер bban (до 30 символов)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4319">Country code (two letters) plus check digits (two digits) plus bban number (up to 30 characters)</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4320">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4320">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4321">Шаблон должен включать в себя все указанные ниже элементы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4321">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4322">Двухбуквенный код страны</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4322">Two-letter country code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4323">Две проверочные цифры (после которых может следовать пробел) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4323">Two check digits (followed by an optional space)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4324">1–7 групп из четырех букв или цифр (могут разделяться пробелами)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4324">1-7 groups of four letters or digits (can be separated by spaces)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4325">1–3 буквы или цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4325">1-3 letters or digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-p131">Формат для названия каждой из стран немного отличается. Тип конфиденциальной информации IBAN применяется к следующим 60 странам:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-p131">The format for each country is slightly different. The IBAN sensitive information type covers these 60 countries:</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4328">ad, ae, al, at, az, ba, be, bg, bh, ch, cr, cy, cz, de, dk, do, ee, es, fi, fo, fr, gb, ge, gi, gl, gr, hr, hu, ie, il, is, it, kw, kz, lb, li, lt, lu, lv, mc, md, me, mk, mr, mt, mu, nl, no, pl, pt, ro, rs, sa, se, si, sk, sm, tn, tr, vg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4328">ad, ae, al, at, az, ba, be, bg, bh, ch, cr, cy, cz, de, dk, do, ee, es, fi, fo, fr, gb, ge, gi, gl, gr, hr, hu, ie, il, is, it, kw, kz, lb, li, lt, lu, lv, mc, md, me, mk, mr, mt, mu, nl, no, pl, pt, ro, rs, sa, se, si, sk, sm, tn, tr, vg</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4329">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4329">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4330">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4330">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4331">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4331">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4332">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4332">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4333">функция Func_iban находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4333">The function Func_iban finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4334">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4334">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="e7dc4711-11b7-4cb0-b88b-2c394a771f0e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_iban" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4335">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4335">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4336">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4336">None</span></span>

   
## <a name="international-classification-of-diseases-icd-10-cm"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4337">Международная классификация Diseases (ICD-10-CM)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4337">International classification of diseases (ICD-10-CM)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4338">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4338">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4339">Dictionary</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4339">Dictionary</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4340">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4340">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4343">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4343">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4344">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4344">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4345">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4345">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4346">Найдено ключевое слово из Dictionary_icd_10_updated.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4346">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_10_updated is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4347">Найдено ключевое слово из Dictionary_icd_10_codes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4347">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_10_codes is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4348">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4348">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4349">Найдено ключевое слово из Dictionary_icd_10_ "Обновлено".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4349">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_10_ updated is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- ICD-10 CM -->
      <Entity id="3356946c-6bb7-449b-b253-6ffa419c0ce7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_10_updated" />
          <Match idRef="Dictionary_icd_10_codes" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_10_updated" />
        </Pattern>

```

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4358">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4358">Pattern</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4362">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4362">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4363">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4363">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4364">Найдено ключевое слово из Dictionary_icd_9_updated.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4364">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_9_updated is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4365">Найдено ключевое слово из Dictionary_icd_9_codes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4365">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_9_codes is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4366">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4366">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4367">Найдено ключевое слово из Dictionary_icd_9_updated.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4367">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_9_updated is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <Entity id="fa3f9c74-ee07-4c52-b5f2-085d6b2c0ec4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_9_updated" />
          <Match idRef="Dictionary_icd_9_codes" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_9_updated" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4368">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4368">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4369">Любой термин из словаря Dictionary_icd_9_updated ключевых слов, основанный на [международной классификации Diseases, девятой редакции, Клиникал модификации (ICD-9-cm)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852605).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4369">Any term from the Dictionary_icd_9_updated keyword dictionary, which is based on the [International Classification of Diseases,Ninth Revision, Clinical Modification (ICD-9-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852605).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4370">Этот тип ищет только термин, а не коды страхования.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4370">This type looks only for the term, not the insurance codes.</span></span>

## <a name="ip-address"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4373">IP-адрес</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4373">IP address</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4374">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4374">Format</span></span>

#### <a name="ipv4"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4375">IPv4</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4375">IPv4:</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4376">Сложный шаблон, ответственный за форматированные (с точками) и неформатированные (без точек) версии IPv4-адресов.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4376">Complex pattern which accounts for formatted (periods) and unformatted (no periods) versions of the IPv4 addresses</span></span>

#### <a name="ipv6"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4377">Поддерживающ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4377">IPv6:</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4378"> Сложный шаблон, ответственный за форматированные номера IPv6 (вместе с двоеточиями).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4378">Complex pattern which accounts for formatted IPv6 numbers (which include colons)</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4379">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4379">Pattern</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4380">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4380">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4381">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4381">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4382">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4382">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4383">В случае с протоколом IPv6 политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4383">For IPv6, a DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4384">регулярное выражение Regex_ipv6_address находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4384">The regular expression Regex_ipv6_address finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4385">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_ipaddress не находится.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4385">No keyword from Keyword_ipaddress is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4386">В случае с протоколом IPv4 политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 95 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4386">For IPv4, a DLP policy is 95% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4387">регулярное выражение Regex_ipv4_address находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4387">The regular expression Regex_ipv4_address finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4388">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ipaddress.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4388">A keyword from Keyword_ipaddress is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4389">В случае с протоколом IPv6 политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 95 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4389">For IPv6, a DLP policy is 95% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4390">регулярное выражение Regex_ipv6_address находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4390">The regular expression Regex_ipv6_address finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4391">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_ipaddress не находится.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4391">No keyword from Keyword_ipaddress is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- IP Address -->
    <Entity id="1daa4ad5-e2dd-4ca4-a788-54722c09efb2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ipv6_address" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_ipaddress" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="95">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ipv4_address" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_ipaddress" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="95">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ipv6_address" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_ipaddress" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4392">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4392">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_ipaddress"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4393">Keyword_ipaddress</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4393">Keyword_ipaddress</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4394">IP (ключевое слово с учетом регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4394">IP (this keyword is case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4395">ip address</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4395">ip address</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4398">IP-כתובת ה</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4398">IP-כתובת ה</span></span> 

## <a name="ireland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4399">Номер водительского удостоверения для Ирландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4399">Ireland driver's license number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4400">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4400">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4401">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4401">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4402">Шесть цифр, за которыми следуют четыре буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4402">Six digits followed by four letters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4403">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4403">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4404">Шесть цифр и четыре буквы:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4404">Six digits and four letters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4405">Шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4405">Six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4406">Четыре буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4406">Four letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4407">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4407">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4408">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4408">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4409">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4409">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4410">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4410">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4411">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4411">The regular expression  `Regex_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4412">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4412">A keyword from  `Keywords_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4413">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4413">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_ireland_eu_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4414">Keywords_ireland_eu_driver "s_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4414">Keywords_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4415">DL #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4415">dl#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4416">driver license</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4416">driver license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4417">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4417">driver license number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4418">Лицензия на драйвер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4418">driver licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4419">Drivers лик.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4419">drivers lic.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4422">driver's license</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4422">driver's license</span></span>

## <a name="ireland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4428">Номер паспорта для Ирландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4428">Ireland passport number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4429">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4429">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4430">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4430">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4431">Две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4431">Two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4432">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4432">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4433">Две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4433">Two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4434">две цифры или буквы (без учета регистра);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4434">Two digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4435">семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4435">Seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4436">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4436">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4437">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4437">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4438">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4438">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4439">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4439">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4440">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4440">The regular expression  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4441">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4441">A keyword from  `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4442">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4442">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4443">Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4443">Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4444">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4444">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4445">Ирландский номер паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4445">irish passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4446">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4446">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4447">соответствующий</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4447">pas</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4448">службу</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4448">passport</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4450">пассепорт нумеро</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4450">passeport numero</span></span>

## <a name="ireland-personal-public-service-pps-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4451">Номер личной общедоступной службы (PPS) Ирландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4451">Ireland personal public service (PPS) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4452">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4452">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4453">Старый формат (до 31 декабря 2012):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4453">Old format (until 31 Dec 2012):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4454">семь цифр, за которыми следует 1-2 букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4454">seven digits followed by 1-2 letters</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4455">Новый формат (1 января 2013 и после):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4455">New format (1 Jan 2013 and after):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4456">семь цифр, за которыми следуют две буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4456">seven digits followed by two letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4457">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4457">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4458">Старый формат (до 31 декабря 2012):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4458">Old format (until 31 Dec 2012):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4459">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4459">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4460">одна-2 буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4460">one to two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4461">Новый формат (1 января 2013 и после):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4461">New format (1 Jan 2013 and after):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4462">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4462">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4463">буква (без учета регистра), которая является буквенной контрольной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4463">a letter (not case sensitive) which is an alphabetic check digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4464">Необязательная буква в диапазоне A – I или "W"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4464">An optional letter in the range A-I, or “W”</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4465">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4465">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4466">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4466">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4467">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4467">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4468">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4468">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4469">Функция Func_ireland_pps находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4469">The function Func_ireland_pps finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4470">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_ireland_eu_national_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4470">A keyword from Keywords_ireland_eu_national_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4471">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4471">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4472">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4472">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4473">функция Func_ireland_pps находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4473">The function Func_ireland_pps finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4474">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4474">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Ireland Personal Public Service (PPS) Number -->
      <Entity id="1cdb674d-c19a-4fcf-9f4b-7f56cc87345a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85" relaxProximity="true">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_ireland_pps" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_ireland_pps" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
