## <a name="israel-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4519">Номер банковского счета для Израиля</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4519">Israel bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4520">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4520">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4521">13 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4521">13 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4522">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4522">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4523">Форматируемые</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4523">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4524">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4524">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4525">тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4525">a dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4526">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4526">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4527">тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4527">a dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4528">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4528">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4529">Неформатированные</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4529">Unformatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4530">	13 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4530">13 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4531">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4531">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4532">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4532">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4533">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4533">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4534">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4534">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4535">регулярное выражение Regex_israel_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4535">The regular expression Regex_israel_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4536">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_israel_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4536">A keyword from Keyword_israel_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Israel Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="7d08b2ff-a0b9-437f-957c-aeddbf9b2b25" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_israel_bank_account_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_israel_bank_account_number" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4537">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4537">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_israel_bank_account_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4538">Keyword_israel_bank_account_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4538">Keyword_israel_bank_account_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4539">Bank Account Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4539">Bank Account Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4540">Bank Account</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4540">Bank Account</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4541">Account Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4541">Account Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4542">מספר חשבון בנק</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4542">מספר חשבון בנק</span></span> 
   
## <a name="israel-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4543">Национальный идентификационный номер Израиля</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4543">Israel national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4544">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4544">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4545">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4545">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4546">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4546">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4547">девять последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4547">nine consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4548">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4548">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4549">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4549">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4550">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4550">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4551">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4551">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4552">функция Func_israeli_national_id_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4552">The function Func_israeli_national_id_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4553">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Israel_National_ID;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4553">A keyword from Keyword_Israel_National_ID is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4554">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4554">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Israel National ID Number -->
<Entity id="e05881f5-1db1-418c-89aa-a3ac5c5277ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_israeli_national_id_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Israel_National_ID" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4555">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4555">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_israel_national_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4556">Keyword_Israel_National_ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4556">Keyword_Israel_National_ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4557">מספר זהות</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4557">מספר זהות</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4558">National ID Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4558">National ID Number</span></span>
   
## <a name="italy-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4559">Номер водительского удостоверения для Италии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4559">Italy driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4560">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в тип конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4560">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4561">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4561">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4562">сочетание из 10 букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4562">a combination of 10 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4563">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4563">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4564">сочетание из 10 букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4564">a combination of 10 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4565">одна буква (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4565">one letter (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4566">буква "A" или "V" (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4566">the letter "A" or "V" (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4567">семь букв (без учета регистра), цифр или символ подчеркивания.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4567">seven letters (not case sensitive), digits, or the underscore character</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4568">одна буква (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4568">one letter (not case sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4569">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4569">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4570">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4570">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4571">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4571">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4572">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4572">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4573">регулярное выражение Regex_italy_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4573">The regular expression Regex_italy_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4574">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4574">A keyword from Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Italy Driver's license Number -->
<Entity id="97d6244f-9157-41bd-8e0c-9d669a5c4d71" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_drivers_license_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4575">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4575">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_italy_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4576">Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4576">Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4577">numero di patente di guida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4577">numero di patente di guida</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4578">patente di guida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4578">patente di guida</span></span> 

## <a name="italy-fiscal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4579">Финансовый код Италии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4579">Italy fiscal code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4580">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4580">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4581">16 – символическое сочетание букв и цифр в указанном шаблоне.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4581">a 16-character combination of letters and digits in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4582">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4582">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4583">16 – буквенное сочетание букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4583">A 16-character combination of letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4584">три буквы, соответствующие первым трем согласным в имени семейства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4584">three letters that correspond to the first three consonants in the family name</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4585">три буквы, соответствующие первым, третьим и четвертым согласным в имени.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4585">three letters that correspond to the first, third, and fourth consonants in the first name</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4586">две цифры, соответствующие последним цифрам года рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4586">two digits that correspond to the last digits of the birth year</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4587">одна буква, соответствующая букве дня рождения, буквы используются в алфавитном порядке, но используются только буквы от A до E, H, L, M, P, R — T (то есть Январь — это R, а Октябрь — R)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4587">one letter that corresponds to the letter for the month of birth—letters are used in alphabetical order, but only the letters A to E, H, L, M, P, R to T are used (thus, January is A and October is R)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4588">две цифры, которые соответствуют дню месяца рождения, для различения пола, 40 добавляется в день рождения для женщин</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4588">two digits that correspond to the day of the month of birth—in order to differentiate between genders, 40 is added to the day of birth for women</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4589">четыре цифры, соответствующие коду города, который относится к органу государственной власти, в котором был создан пользователь, (для иностранных стран используются коды уровня страны).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4589">four digits that corresponds to the area code specific to the municipality where the person was born (country-wide codes are used for foreign countries)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4590">одна цифра четности</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4590">one parity digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4591">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4591">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4592">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4592">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4593">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4593">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4594">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4594">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4595">Функция  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4595">The function  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4596">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4596">A keyword from  `Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4597">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4597">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4598">Функция  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4598">The function  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Italy Fiscal Code -->
      <Entity id="4cd79172-8da9-4ff5-9188-98b1e7e2eca6" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4599">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4599">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4600">Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4600">Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4601">налоговые кости</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4601">codice fiscal</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4602">финансовый отчет по сокостям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4602">codice fiscale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4603">личные коды для сокодовых костей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4603">codice id personale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4604">Персональные подкодеки</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4604">codice personale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4605">Финансовый код</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4605">fiscal code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4606">Нумеро цертификато персональный</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4606">numero certificato personale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4607">Нумеро di идентификазионе Фин.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4607">numero di identificazione fiscale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4608">личный идентификатор нумеро</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4608">numero id personale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4609">персональные настройки нумеро</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4609">numero personale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4610">личный номер сертификата</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4610">personal certificate number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4611">персональный код</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4611">personal code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4612">личный код</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4612">personal id code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4613">личный идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4613">personal id number</span></span>

## <a name="italy-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4633">Номер паспорта для Италии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4633">Italy passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4634">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4634">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4635">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4635">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4636">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4636">two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4637">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4637">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4638">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4638">two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4639">две цифры или буквы (без учета регистра).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4639">two digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4640">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4640">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4641">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4641">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4642">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4642">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4643">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4643">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4644">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4644">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4645">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4645">The regular expression  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4646">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4646">A keyword from  `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4647">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4647">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_italy_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4648">Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4648">Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4649">номер паспорта для итальянского языка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4649">italian passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4650">Репубблика итальянский пассапорто</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4650">repubblica italiana passaporto</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4651">пассапорто</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4651">passaporto</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4652">пассапорто итальянский</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4652">passaporto italiana</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4653">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4653">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4654">Итальянский пассапорто нумеро</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4654">italiana passaporto numero</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4655">пассапорто нумеро</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4655">passaporto numero</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4656">нумéро пассепорт италиен</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4656">numéro passeport italien</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4657">нумéро пассепорт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4657">numéro passeport</span></span>


## <a name="italy-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4658">Налоговый номер добавленной стоимости (Италия)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4658">Italy value added tax number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4659">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4659">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4660">13-буквенно-цифровой буквенный шаблон с необязательными ограничителями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4660">13 character alphanumeric pattern with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4661">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4661">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4662">13-буквенно-цифровой буквенно-цифровой шаблон с необязательными ограничителями:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4662">13 character alphanumeric pattern with optional delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4663">I или i</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4663">I or i</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4664">T или t</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4664">T or t</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4665">необязательный пробел, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4665">optional space, dot, hyphen or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4666">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4666">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4667">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4667">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4668">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4668">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4669">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4669">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4670">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4670">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4671">Функция Func_italy_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4671">The function Func_italy_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4672">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4672">A keyword from Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4673">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4673">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4674">Функция Func_italy_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4674">The function Func_italy_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Italy Value Added Tax -->
      <Entity id="26a8cc07-2283-4a2a-ab1d-4ab643c4c67f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4675">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4675">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_italy_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4676">Keyword_italy_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4676">Keyword_italy_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4677">номер НДС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4677">vat number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4678">НДС No</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4678">vat no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4679">процент #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4679">vat#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4680">ива</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4680">iva</span></span>

## <a name="japan-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4682">Номер банковского счета для Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4682">Japan bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4683">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4683">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4684">семь или восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4684">seven or eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4685">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4685">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4686">номер банковского счета:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4686">bank account number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4687">семь или восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4687">seven or eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4688">код филиала банковского счета:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4688">bank account branch code:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4689">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4689">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4690">пробел или тире (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4690">a space or dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4691">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4691">three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4692">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4692">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4693">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4693">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4694">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4694">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4695">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4695">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4696">Функция Func_jp_bank_account находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4696">The function Func_jp_bank_account finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4697">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_account.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4697">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_account is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4698">Верно одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4698">One of the following is true:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4699">функция Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4699">The function Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4700">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4700">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4701">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4701">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4702">функция Func_jp_bank_account находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4702">The function Func_jp_bank_account finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4703">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_account.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4703">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_account is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="d354f95b-96ee-4b80-80bc-4377312b55bc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Version minEngineVersion="15.01.0131.000">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_bank_account" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_account" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code" />
          </Any>
      </Pattern>
  </Version>    
     <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_bank_account" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_account" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4704">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4704">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_bank_account"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4705">Keyword_jp_bank_account</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4705">Keyword_jp_bank_account</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4706">Checking Account Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4706">Checking Account Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4707">Checking Account</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4707">Checking Account</span></span>

## <a name="japan-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4762">Номер водительского удостоверения для Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4762">Japan driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4763">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4763">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4764">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4764">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4765">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4765">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4766">12 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4766">12 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4767">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4767">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4768">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4768">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4769">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4769">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4770">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4770">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4771">функция Func_jp_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4771">The function Func_jp_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4772">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4772">A keyword from Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="c6011143-d087-451c-8313-7f6d4aed2270" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef ="Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="japan-my-number---corporate"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4800">Мой номер для Японии — корпоративный</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4800">Japan My Number - Corporate</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4801">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4801">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4802">13 цифра, цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4802">13 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4803">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4803">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4804">13 цифра:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4804">13 digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4805">одна цифра от 1 до девяти</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4805">one digit from one to nine</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4806">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4806">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4807">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4807">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4808">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4808">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4809">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4809">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4810">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4810">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4811">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_corporate находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4811">The function Func_japanese_my_number_corporate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4812">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4812">A keyword from Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4813">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4813">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4814">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_corporate находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4814">The function Func_japanese_my_number_corporate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Japanese My Number – Corporate -->
      <Entity id="9e0eaf79-ff20-4ffb-b3e4-e7368d5db6ff" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4815">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4815">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_japan_my_number_corporate"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4816">Keyword_japan_my_number_corporate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4816">Keyword_japan_my_number_corporate</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4817">корпоративный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4817">corporate number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4818">マイナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4818">マイナンバー</span></span>

## <a name="japan-my-number---personal"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4827">Япония мой номер — личное</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4827">Japan My Number - Personal</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4828">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4828">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4829">12 цифр номера</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4829">12 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4830">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4830">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4831">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4831">12 digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4832">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4832">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4833">необязательный пробел, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4833">an optional space, dot or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4834">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4834">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4835">необязательный пробел, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4835">an optional space, dot or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4836">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4836">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4837">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4837">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4838">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4838">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4839">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4839">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4840">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4840">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4841">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_personal находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4841">The function Func_japanese_my_number_personal finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4842">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4842">A keyword from Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4843">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4843">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4844">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_personal находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4844">The function Func_japanese_my_number_personal finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Japanese My Number – Personal -->
      <Entity id="98da8e66-7299-4ebd-9f82-c871ab37d3ef" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_personal" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_personal" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4845">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4845">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4849">個人番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4849">個人番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4850">共通番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4850">共通番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4851">マイナンバーカード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4851">マイナンバーカード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4852">マイナンバーカード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4852">マイナンバーカード番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4853">個人番号カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4853">個人番号カード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4854">個人識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4854">個人識別番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4855">個人識別ナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4855">個人識別ナンバー</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4856">通知カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4856">通知カード</span></span>

   
## <a name="japan-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4857">Номер паспорта для Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4857">Japan passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4858">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4858">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4859">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4859">two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4860">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4860">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4861">две буквы (без учета регистра), за которыми следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4861">two letters (not case sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4862">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4862">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4863">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4863">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4864">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4864">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4865">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4865">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4866">функция Func_jp_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4866">The function Func_jp_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4867">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4867">A keyword from Keyword_jp_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Passport Number -->
<Entity id="75177310-1a09-4613-bf6d-833aae3743f8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_passport" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_passport" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4868">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4868">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_passport"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4869">Keyword_jp_passport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4869">Keyword_jp_passport</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4870">パスポート</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4870">パスポート</span></span>

## <a name="japan-residence-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4874">Номер карточки для Японии (Япония)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4874">Japan residence card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4875">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4875">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4876">12 букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4876">12 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4877">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4877">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4878">12 букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4878">12 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4879">две буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4879">two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4880">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4880">eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4881">две буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4881">two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4882">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4882">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4883">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4883">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4884">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4884">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4885">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4885">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4886">Регулярное выражение Regex_jp_residence_card_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4886">The regular expression Regex_jp_residence_card_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4887">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_residence_card_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4887">A keyword from Keyword_jp_residence_card_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Japan Residence Card Number-->
-<Entity id="ac36fef2-a289-4e2c-bb48-b02366e89fc0" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Regex_jp_residence_card_number"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_residence_card_number"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4888">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4888">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_residence_card_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4889">Keyword_jp_residence_card_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4889">Keyword_jp_residence_card_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4890">Номер карточки проживания</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4890">Residence card number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4891">Номер карточки проживания</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4891">Residence card no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4892">Карточка проживания #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4892">Residence card #</span></span>

## <a name="japan-resident-registration-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4894">Номер резидентного регистрационного номера для Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4894">Japan resident registration number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4895">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4895">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4896">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4896">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4897">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4897">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4898">11 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4898">11 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4899">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4899">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4900">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4900">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4901">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4901">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4902">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4902">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4903">функция Func_jp_resident_registration_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4903">The function Func_jp_resident_registration_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4904">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4904">A keyword from Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Resident Registration Number -->
<Entity id="01c1209b-6389-4faf-a5f8-3f7e13899652" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_resident_registration_number" />
        <Match idRef ="Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4905">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4905">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4908">Resident Register Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4908">Resident Register Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4909">Residents Basic Registry Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4909">Residents Basic Registry Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4910">Resident Registration No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4910">Resident Registration No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4911">Resident Register No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4911">Resident Register No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4912">Residents Basic Registry No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4912">Residents Basic Registry No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4913">Basic Resident Register No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4913">Basic Resident Register No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4914">住民登録番号 、 登録番号をレジデント</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4914">住民登録番号、登録番号をレジデント</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4915">住民基本登録番号 、 登録番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4915">住民基本登録番号、登録番号</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4916">住民基本レジストリ番号を常駐</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4916">住民基本レジストリ番号を常駐</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4917">登録番号を常駐住民基本台帳登録番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4917">登録番号を常駐住民基本台帳登録番号</span></span> 

   
## <a name="japan-social-insurance-number-sin"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4918">Номер социального страхования для Японии (SIN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4918">Japan social insurance number (SIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4919">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4919">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4920">7–12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4920">7-12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4921">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4921">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4922">7–12 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4922">7-12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4923">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4923">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4924">дефис (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4924">a hyphen (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4925">шесть цифр или</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4925">six digits OR</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4926">7–12 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4926">7-12 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4927">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4927">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4928">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4928">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4929">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4929">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4930">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4930">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4931">функция Func_jp_sin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4931">The function Func_jp_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4932">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_sin.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4932">A keyword from Keyword_jp_sin is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4933">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4933">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4934">функция Func_jp_sin_pre_1997 находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4934">The function Func_jp_sin_pre_1997 finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4935">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_sin.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4935">A keyword from Keyword_jp_sin is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Social Insurance Number -->
<Entity id="c840e719-0896-45bb-84fd-1ed5c95e45ff" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_sin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_sin" />
    </Pattern>
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_sin_pre_1997" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_sin" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4936">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4936">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_sin"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4937">Keyword_jp_sin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4937">Keyword_jp_sin</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4938">Social Insurance No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4938">Social Insurance No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4939">Social Insurance Num</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4939">Social Insurance Num</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4940">Social Insurance Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4940">Social Insurance Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4941">社会保険のテンキー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4941">社会保険のテンキー</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4942">社会保険番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4942">社会保険番号</span></span> 

## <a name="latvia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4943">Номер водительского удостоверения для Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4943">Latvia driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4944">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4944">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4945">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4945">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4946">три буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4946">three letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4947">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4947">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4948">три буквы и шесть цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4948">three letters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4949">три буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4949">three letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4950">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4950">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4951">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4951">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4952">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4952">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4953">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4953">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4954">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4954">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4955">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4955">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4956">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4956">A keyword from  `Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4957">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4957">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_latvia_eu_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4958">Keywords_latvia_eu_driver "s_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4958">Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4959">DL #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4959">dl#</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4961">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4961">driver license number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4962">Лицензия на драйвер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4962">driver licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4963">Drivers лик.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4963">drivers lic.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4964">drivers license</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4964">drivers license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4965">drivers licence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4965">drivers licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4966">driver's license</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4966">driver's license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4967">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4967">driver's license number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4968">номер лицензии на драйвер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4968">driver's licence number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4969">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4969">driving license number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4970">длно #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4970">dlno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4971">аутовадīтāжа аплиекīба</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4971">autovadītāja apliecība</span></span>

## <a name="latvia-personal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4972">Личный код Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4972">Latvia personal code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4973">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4973">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4974">11 цифр и необязательный дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4974">11 digits and an optional hyphen</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4975">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4975">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4976">Старый формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4976">Old format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4977">11 цифр и дефис:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4977">11 digits and a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4978">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (ДДММГГ —)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4978">six digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMYY)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4979">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4979">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4980">одна цифра, соответствующая столетию рождения ("0" для 19 века, "1" для 20-й век) и "2" для 21 века)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4980">one digit that corresponds to the century of birth ("0" for 19th century, "1" for 20th century, and "2" for 21st century)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4981">четыре цифры, созданные случайным образом</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4981">four digits, randomly generated</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4982">Новый формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4982">New format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4983">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4983">11 digits</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4984">Две цифры "32"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4984">Two digits "32"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4985">девять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4985">Nine digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4986">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4986">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4987">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4987">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4988">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4988">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4989">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4989">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4990">Функция  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` или регулярное выражение `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` выполняет поиск содержимого, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4990">The function  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` or the regex `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4991">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4991">A keyword from  `Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4992">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4992">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4993">Функция  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` или регулярное выражение `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` выполняет поиск содержимого, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4993">The function  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` or the regex `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Latvia Personal Code -->
      <Entity id="03fcf763-27c2-49ed-9422-2641c6c895c9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4994">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4994">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4995">Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4995">Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4996">Административный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4996">administrative number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4997">алвас нē</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4997">alvas nē</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4998">номер рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4998">birth number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-4999">номер для согражданства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-4999">citizen number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5000">гражданское число</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5000">civil number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5001">номер электронного переписи</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5001">electronic census number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5002">электронный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5002">electronic number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5003">Финансовый код</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5003">fiscal code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5004">номер пользователя для сферы здравоохранения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5004">healthcare user number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5005">кодов #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5005">id#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5006">ID — код</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5006">id-code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5007">identification number
