## <a name="latvia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5056">Номер паспорта для Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5056">Latvia passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5057">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5057">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5058">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5058">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5059">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5059">two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5060">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5060">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5061">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5061">two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5062">две цифры или буквы (без учета регистра).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5062">two digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5063">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5063">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5064">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5064">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5065">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5065">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5066">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5066">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5067">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5067">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5068">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5068">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5069">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5069">A keyword from  `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5070">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5070">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5071">Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5071">Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5072">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5072">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5073">номер паспорта для Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5073">latvian passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5074">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5074">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5075">ПАСЕ нумурс</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5075">pase numurs</span></span>    


## <a name="lithuania-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5076">Литва номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5076">Lithuania driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5077">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5077">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5078">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5078">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5079">восемь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5079">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5080">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5080">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5081">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5081">eight digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5082">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5082">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5083">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5083">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5084">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5084">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5085">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5085">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5086">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5086">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5087">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5087">A keyword from  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5088">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5088">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_lithuania_eu_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5089">Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver "s_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5089">Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5093">Лицензия на драйвер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5093">driver licence</span></span>

## <a name="lithuania-personal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5103">Литва персональный код</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5103">Lithuania personal code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5104">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5104">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5105">11 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5105">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5106">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5106">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5107">11 цифр без пробелов и разделителей:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5107">11 digits without spaces and delimiters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5108">одна цифра (1-6), соответствующая пол и век рождения человека</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5108">one digit (1-6) that corresponds to the person's gender and century of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5109">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (ГГММДД)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5109">six digits that correspond to birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5110">три цифры, которые соответствуют серийному числу даты рождения.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5110">three digits that correspond to the serial number of the date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5111">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5111">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5112">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5112">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5113">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5113">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5114">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5114">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5115">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5115">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5116">Функция  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5116">The function  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5117">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5117">A keyword from  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5118">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5118">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5119">Функция  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5119">The function  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Personal Code -->
      <Entity id="cd6d3786-8ec3-4524-a2cf-1e0095379171" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="lithuania-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5154">Литва номер паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5154">Lithuania passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5155">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5155">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5156">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5156">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5157">восемь цифр или букв без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5157">eight digits or letters with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5158">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5158">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5159">восемь цифр или букв (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5159">eight digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5160">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5160">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5161">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5161">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5162">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5162">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5163">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5163">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5164">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5164">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5165">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5165">A keyword from  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5166">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5166">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5167">Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5167">Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5168">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5168">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5169">номер паспорта лисуниан</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5169">lithunian passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5170">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5170">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5171">Пасо нумерис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5171">paso numeris</span></span>


## <a name="luxemburg-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5172">Номер водительского удостоверения Луксембург</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5172">Luxemburg driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5173">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5173">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5174">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5174">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5175">шесть цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5175">six digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5176">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5176">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5177">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5177">six digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5178">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5178">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5179">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5179">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5180">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5180">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5181">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5181">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5182">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5182">The regular expression  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5183">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5183">A keyword from  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-national-identification-number-natural-persons"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5199">Национальный идентификационный номер Луксембург (для природных людей)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5199">Luxemburg national identification number (natural persons)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5200">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5200">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5201">13 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5201">13 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5202">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5202">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5203">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5203">13 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5204">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5204">11 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5205">две контрольные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5205">two check digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5206">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5206">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5207">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5207">yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5208">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5208">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5209">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5209">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5210">Функция  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5210">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5211">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5211">A keyword from  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5212">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5212">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5213">Функция  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5213">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 


```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg National Identification Number (Natural persons) -->
      <Entity id="aaf661ed-29ec-426d-8bf9-880cad298ebb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5236">Номер паспорта Луксембург</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5236">Luxemburg passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5237">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5237">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5238">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5238">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5239">восемь цифр или букв без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5239">eight digits or letters with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5240">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5240">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5241">восемь цифр или букв (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5241">eight digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5242">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5242">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5243">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5243">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5244">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5244">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5245">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5245">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5246">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_nation_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5246">The regular expression  `Regex_nation_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5247">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_nation_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5247">A keyword from  `Keywords_nation_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_nation_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_nation_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5248">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5248">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5253">пасснуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5253">passnummer</span></span>

## <a name="luxemburg-national-identification-number-non-natural-persons"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5254">Луксембург Национальный идентификационный номер (неестественные пользователи)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5254">Luxemburg national identification number (non natural persons)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5255">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5255">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5256">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5256">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5257">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5257">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5258">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5258">11 digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5259">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5259">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5260">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5260">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5261">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5261">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5262">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5262">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5263">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5263">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5264">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5264">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5265">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5265">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5266">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5266">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5267">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5267">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5268">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5268">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5269">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5269">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5270">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5270">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5271">Функция  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5271">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5272">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5272">A keyword from  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5273">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5273">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5274">Функция  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5274">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg National Identification Number (Non-natural persons) -->
      <Entity id="84bffa3a-d805-4788-a613-b1e4df3804cf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="malaysia-identification-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5314">Идентификационный номер карты Малайзии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5314">Malaysia identification card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5315">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5315">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5316">12 цифр, содержащих необязательные дефисы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5316">12 digits containing optional hyphens</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5317">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5317">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5318">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5318">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5319">шесть цифр в формате ГГММДД Дата рождения;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5319">six digits in the format YYMMDD which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5320">тире (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5320">a dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5321">код места рождения из двух букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5321">two-letter place-of-birth code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5322">тире (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5322">a dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5323">три случайные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5323">three random digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5324">код пола из одной цифры;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5324">one-digit gender code</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5325">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5325">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5326">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5326">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5327">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5327">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5328">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5328">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5329">регулярное выражение Regex_malaysia_id_card_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5329">The regular expression Regex_malaysia_id_card_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5330">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5330">A keyword from Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Malaysia ID Card Number -->
</Entity>
      <Entity id="7f0e921c-9677-435b-aba2-bb8f1013c749" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
            <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malaysia_id_card_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5344">кад апликаси Digital</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5344">kad aplikasi digital</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5345">кад пенженалан Малайзии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5345">kad pengenalan malaysia</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5346">ключев</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5346">kp</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5347">ключевой номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5347">kp no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5348">микад</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5348">mykad</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5349">микас</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5349">mykas</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5350">микид</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5350">mykid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5351">мипр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5351">mypr</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5352">митентера</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5352">mytentera</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5353">идентификационная карточка Малайзии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5353">malaysia identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5354">идентификационная карточка малайсиан</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5354">malaysian identity card</span></span>

## <a name="malta-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5357">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Мальта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5357">Malta driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5358">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5358">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5359">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5359">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5360">Сочетание двух символов и шести цифр в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5360">Combination of two characters and six digits in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5361">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5361">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5362">сочетание двух символов и шести цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5362">combination of two characters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5363">два символа (цифры или буквы без учета регистра);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5363">two characters (digits or letters, not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5364">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5364">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5365">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5365">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5366">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5366">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5367">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5367">three digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5368">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5368">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5369">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5369">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5370">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5370">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5371">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5371">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5372">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5372">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5373">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5373">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
<!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
 <Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5374">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5374">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_malta_eu_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5375">Keywords_malta_eu_driver "s_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5375">Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5376">DL #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5376">dl#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5377">driver license</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5377">driver license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5378">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5378">driver license number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5379">Лицензия на драйвер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5379">driver licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5380">Drivers лик.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5380">drivers lic.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5381">drivers license</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5381">drivers license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5382">drivers licence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5382">drivers licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5383">driver's license</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5383">driver's license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5384">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5384">driver's license number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5385">номер лицензии на драйвер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5385">driver's licence number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5386">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5386">driving license number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5387">длно #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5387">dlno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5388">лиċензжаные зада Севкан</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5388">liċenzja tas-sewqan</span></span>

## <a name="malta-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5389">Номер идентификационной карточки Мальта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5389">Malta identity card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5390">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5390">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5391">семь цифр, за которыми следует одна буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5391">seven digits followed by one letter</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5392">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5392">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5393">семь цифр, за которыми следует одна буква:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5393">seven digits followed by one letter:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5394">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5394">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5395">одна буква в письмах "M, G, A, P, L, H, B, Z" (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5395">one letter in "M, G, A, P, L, H, B, Z" (case insensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5396">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5396">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5397">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5397">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5398">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5398">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5399">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5399">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5400">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5400">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5401">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5401">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5402">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5402">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5403">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5403">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Identity Card Number -->
      <Entity id="854b36b3-a388-4ac8-a4ec-677c2b5e4356" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="malta-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5420">Номер паспорта для Мальта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5420">Malta passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5421">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5421">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5422">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5422">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5423">семь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5423">seven digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5424">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5424">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5425">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5425">seven digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5426">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5426">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5427">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5427">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5428">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5428">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5429">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5429">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5430">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5430">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5431">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5431">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5432">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5432">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_malta_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5433">Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5433">Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5434">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5434">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5435">номер паспорта Мальтийский</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5435">maltese passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5436">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5436">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5437">нумру Тал — пассапорт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5437">numru tal-passaport</span></span>

## <a name="malta-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5438">Идентификационный номер налога Мальта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5438">Malta tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5439">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5439">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5440">Для национальных Мальтийский:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5440">For Maltese nationals:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5441">семь цифр и одна буква в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5441">seven digits and one letter in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5442">Мальтийскийные страны и Мальтийский, не являющиеся субъектами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5442">Non-Maltese nationals and Maltese entities:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5443">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5443">nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5444">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5444">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5445">Мальтийский Nationals: семь цифр и одна буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5445">Maltese nationals: seven digits and one letter</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5446">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5446">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5447">одна буква (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5447">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5448">Мальтийскийные страны и Мальтийский, не связанные с организациями: девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5448">Non-Maltese nationals and Maltese entities: nine digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5449">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5449">nine digits</span></span> 
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5450">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5450">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5451">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5451">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5452">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5452">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5453">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5453">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5454">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number`  или `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` ищет содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5454">The regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number`  or `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5455">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5455">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5456">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5456">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5457">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number` или `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` ищет содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5457">The regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number` or `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Tax ID Number -->
      <Entity id="ec830c63-65f4-45d0-9d8c-910dc8334b20" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-citizens-service-bsn-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5490">Номер службы (BSN) для Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5490">Netherlands citizen's service (BSN) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5491">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5491">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5492">восемь девяти цифр, содержащих необязательные пробелы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5492">eight-nine digits containing optional spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5493">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5493">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5494">восемь девяти цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5494">eight-nine digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5495">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5495">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5496">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5496">a space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5497">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5497">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5498">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5498">a space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5499">две три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5499">two-three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5500">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5500">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5501">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5501">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5502">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5502">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5503">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5503">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5504">функция Func_netherlands_bsn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5504">The function Func_netherlands_bsn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5505">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_netherlands_bsn;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5505">A keyword from Keyword_netherlands_bsn is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5506">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5506">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Citizen's Service (BSN) Number -->
      <Entity id="c5f54253-ef7e-44f6-a578-440ed67e946d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_bsn" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5530">Номер водительского удостоверения для Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5530">Netherlands driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5531">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5531">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5532">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5532">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5533">десять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5533">ten digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5534">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5534">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5535">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5535">ten digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5536">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5536">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5537">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5537">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5538">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5538">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5539">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5539">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5540">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5540">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5541">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5541">A keyword from  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5559">Номер паспорта Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5559">Netherlands passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5560">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5560">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5561">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5561">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5562">девять букв или цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5562">nine letters or digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5563">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5563">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5564">девять букв или цифр;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5564">nine letters or digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5565">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5565">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5566">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5566">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5567">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5567">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5568">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5568">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5569">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5569">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5570">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5570">A keyword from  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5571">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5571">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5574">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5574">passport number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5576">недерланден паспурт нуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5576">nederlanden paspoort nummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5577">паспурт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5577">paspoort</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5578">недерланден паспуртнуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5578">nederlanden paspoortnummer</span></span>

## <a name="netherlands-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5580">Идентификационный номер налога Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5580">Netherlands tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5581">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5581">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5582">девять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5582">nine digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5583">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5583">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5584">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5584">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5585">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5585">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5586">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5586">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5587">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5587">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5588">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5588">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5589">Функция  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5589">The function  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5590">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5590">A keyword from  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5591">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5591">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5592">Функция  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5592">The function  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="01f42a64-eba7-4892-a67b-398237e4ade2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5593">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5593">Keywords</span></span>
