## <a name="netherlands-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5630">Номер налога добавленных значений в Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5630">Netherlands value added tax number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5631">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5631">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5632">14-буквенно-буквенно-цифровой шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5632">14 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5633">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5633">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5634">14-буквенно-буквенно-символьный шаблон:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5634">14-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5635">N или n</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5635">N or n</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5636">L или l</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5636">L or l</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5637">необязательный пробел, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5637">optional space, dot or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5638">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5638">nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5639">необязательный пробел, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5639">optional space, dot or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5640">B или b</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5640">B or b</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5641">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5641">two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5642">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5642">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5643">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5643">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5644">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5644">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5645">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5645">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5646">Функция Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5646">The function Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5647">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5647">A keyword from Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5648">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5648">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5649">Функция Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5649">The function Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="4f320d9b-4972-41ae-b337-88d499bb1ade" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5650">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5650">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_netherlands_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5651">Keyword_netherlands_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5651">Keyword_netherlands_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5652">номер НДС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5652">vat number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5653">НДС No</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5653">vat no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5654">процент #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5654">vat#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5655">веарде тафоеже налога на жетал</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5655">wearde tafoege tax getal</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5656">БТВ нûмер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5656">btw nûmer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5657">БТВ — нуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5657">btw-nummer</span></span>


## <a name="new-zealand-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5658">Номер банковского счета Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5658">New Zealand bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5659">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5659">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5660">шаблон с 14 до 16 цифр с необязательным разделителем</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5660">14 to 16 digit pattern with optional delimiter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5661">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5661">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5662">шаблон с 14 до 16 цифр с необязательным разделителем:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5662">14 to 16 digit pattern with optional delimiter:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5663">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5663">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5664">Необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5664">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5665">от трех до четырех цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5665">three to four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5666">Необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5666">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5667">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5667">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5668">Необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5668">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5669">две до трех цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5669">two to three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5670">Параметры дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5670">an options hyphen or space</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5671">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5671">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5672">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5672">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5673">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5673">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5674">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5674">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5675">Функция Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5675">The function Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5676">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_new_zealand_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5676">A keyword from Keywords_new_zealand_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5677">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5677">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5678">Функция Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5678">The function Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Bank Account Number -->
      <Entity id="1a97fc2b-dd2f-48f1-bc4e-2ddf25813956" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_new_zealand_bank_account_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5679">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5679">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_new_zealand_bank_account_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5680">Keyword_new_zealand_bank_account_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5680">Keyword_new_zealand_bank_account_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5681">номер счета</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5681">account number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5683">bank_acct_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5683">bank_acct_id</span></span>

## <a name="new-zealand-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5686">Номер водительского удостоверения для Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5686">New Zealand driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5687">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5687">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5688">8-буквенно-цифровой шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5688">eight character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5689">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5689">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5690">8-буквенно-цифровой шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5690">eight character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5691">две буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5691">two letters</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5692">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5692">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5693">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5693">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5694">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5694">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5695">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5695">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5696">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5696">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5697">Функция Func_newzealand_driver_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5697">The function Func_newzealand_driver_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5698">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5698">A keyword from Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5699">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5699">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5700">Функция Func_newzealand_driver_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5700">The function Func_newzealand_driver_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Driver License Number -->
      <Entity id="1924b377-d287-49c9-a737-cfe7a8a2615a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="new-zealand-inland-revenue-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5767">Номер дохода по некоторому контакту для Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5767">New Zealand inland revenue number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5768">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5768">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5769">восемь или девять цифр с необязательными ограничителями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5769">eight or nine digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5770">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5770">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5771">восемь или девять цифр с необязательными ограничителями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5771">eight or nine digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5772">две или три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5772">two or three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5773">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5773">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5774">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5774">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5775">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5775">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5776">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5776">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5777">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5777">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5778">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5778">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5779">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5779">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5780">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5780">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5781">Функция Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5781">The function Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5782">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5782">A keyword from Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5783">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5783">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5784">Функция Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5784">The function Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Inland Revenue Number -->
      <Entity id="dd0fe2bc-7bcf-455f-bac1-83b1e3eb25fd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5785">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5785">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5786">Keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5786">Keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5787">ИРД но.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5787">ird no.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5789">NZ ИРД</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5789">nz ird</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5790">Новая Зеландия ИРД</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5790">new zealand ird</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5791">номер ИРД</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5791">ird number</span></span>

## <a name="new-zealand-ministry-of-health-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5793">Номер министерства здоровья Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5793">New Zealand ministry of health number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5794">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5794">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5795">три буквы, пробел (необязательно) и четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5795">three letters, a space (optional), and four digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5796">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5796">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5797">три буквы (без учета регистра), пробел (необязательно) из четырех цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5797">three letters (not case sensitive) a space (optional) four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5798">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5798">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5799">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5799">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5800">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5800">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5801">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5801">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5802">функция Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5802">The function Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5803">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_nz_terms;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5803">A keyword from Keyword_nz_terms is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5804">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5804">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- New Zealand Health Number -->
<Entity id="2b71c1c8-d14e-4430-82dc-fd1ed6bf05c7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_nz_terms" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5805">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5805">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_nz_terms"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5806">Keyword_nz_terms</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5806">Keyword_nz_terms</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5807">нхи</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5807">NHI</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5808">Новая Зеландия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5808">New Zealand</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5809">Здравоохранение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5809">Health</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5810">обращения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5810">treatment</span></span> 


## <a name="new-zealand-social-wlefare-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5811">Номер социального влефареа Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5811">New Zealand social wlefare number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5812">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5812">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5813">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5813">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5814">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5814">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5815">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5815">nine digits</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5816">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5816">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5817">Необязательный перенос</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5817">an optional hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5818">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5818">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5819">Необязательный перенос</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5819">an optional hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5820">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5820">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5821">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5821">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5822">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5822">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5823">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5823">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5824">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5824">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5825">Функция Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5825">The function Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5826">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5826">A keyword from Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5827">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5827">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5828">Функция Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5828">The function Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Newzealand Social Welfare Number -->
      <Entity id="20f3c48d-4ac1-4cd2-86bd-34ecc1826e9d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
    </Version>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5829">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5829">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5830">Keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5830">Keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5831">социальные велфаре #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5831">social welfare #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5832">социальные велфаре #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5832">social welfare#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5833">социальное велфаре No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5833">social welfare No.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5834">номер социального велфаре</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5834">social welfare number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5835">свн #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5835">swn#</span></span>

   
## <a name="norway-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5836">Идентификационный номер Норвегии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5836">Norway identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5837">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5837">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5838">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5838">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5839">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5839">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5840">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5840">11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5841">шесть цифр в формате ддммгг — Дата рождения;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5841">six digits in the format DDMMYY which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5842">индивидуальный номер из трех цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5842">three-digit individual number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5843">две контрольные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5843">two check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5844">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5844">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5845">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5845">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5846">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5846">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5847">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5847">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5848">функция Func_norway_id_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5848">The function Func_norway_id_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5849">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_norway_id_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5849">A keyword from Keyword_norway_id_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5850">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5850">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5851">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5851">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5852">функция Func_norway_id_numbe находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5852">The function Func_norway_id_numbe finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5853">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5853">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Norway Identification Number -->
<Entity id="d4c8a798-e9f2-4bd3-9652-500d24080fc3" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_norway_id_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_norway_id_number"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_norway_id_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5854">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5854">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_norway_id_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5855">Keyword_norway_id_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5855">Keyword_norway_id_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5856">Personal identification number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5856">Personal identification number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5858">ID Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5858">ID Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5859">Процедура</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5859">Identification</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5860">персоннуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5860">Personnummer</span></span>

## <a name="philippines-unified-multi-purpose-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5862">Идентификационный номер единой системы для различных целей Филиппины</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5862">Philippines unified multi-purpose identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5863">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5863">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5864">12 цифр, разделенных дефисами.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5864">12 digits separated by hyphens</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5865">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5865">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5866">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5866">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5867">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5867">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5868">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5868">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5869">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5869">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5870">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5870">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5871">одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5871">one digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5872">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5872">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5873">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5873">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5874">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5874">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5875">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5875">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5876">регулярное выражение Regex_philippines_unified_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5876">The regular expression Regex_philippines_unified_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5877">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_philippines_id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5877">A keyword from Keyword_philippines_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Philippines Unified Multi-Purpose ID number -->
<Entity id="019b39dd-8c25-4765-91a3-d9c6baf3c3b3" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_philippines_unified_id"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_philippines_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5878">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5878">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_philippines_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5879">Keyword_philippines_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5879">Keyword_philippines_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5880">Unified Multi-Purpose ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5880">Unified Multi-Purpose ID</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5881">умид</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5881">UMID</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5882">Identity Card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5882">Identity Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5883">Pinag-isang Multi-Layunin ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5883">Pinag-isang Multi-Layunin ID</span></span>

## <a name="poland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5884">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5884">Poland driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5885">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5885">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5886">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5886">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5887">14 цифр, содержащих 2 косых черты.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5887">14 digits containing 2 forward slashes</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5888">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5888">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5889">14 цифр и 2 косых черт:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5889">14 digits and 2 forward slashes:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5890">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5890">five digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5891">косая черта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5891">a forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5892">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5892">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5893">косая черта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5893">a forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5894">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5894">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5895">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5895">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5896">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5896">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5897">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5897">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5898">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5898">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5899">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5899">The regular expression  `Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5900">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5900">A keyword from  `Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="poland-identity-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5916">Идентификационная карточка Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5916">Poland identity card</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5917">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5917">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5918">три буквы и шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5918">three letters and six digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5919">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5919">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5920">три буквы (без учета регистра), за которыми следуют шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5920">three letters (not case sensitive) followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5921">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5921">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5922">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5922">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5923">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5923">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5924">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5924">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5925">функция Func_polish_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5925">The function Func_polish_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5926">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5926">A keyword from Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5927">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5927">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Poland Identity Card-->
<Entity id="25E64989-ED5D-40CA-A939-6C14183BB7BF" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number" />
      </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5928">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5928">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5929">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5929">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5931">Нумер доводу особистего</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5931">Numer dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5932">Назва i нумер доводу особистего</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5932">Nazwa i numer dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5933">Назва i НР доводу особистего</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5933">Nazwa i nr dowodu osobistego</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5935">Dowód Tożsamości</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5935">Dowód Tożsamości</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5936">Dow.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5936">dow.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5937">совместим.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5937">os.</span></span>

   
## <a name="poland-national-id-pesel"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5938">Национальный идентификатор Польша (PESEL)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5938">Poland national ID (PESEL)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5939">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5939">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5940">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5940">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5941">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5941">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5942">6 цифр, представляющих дату рождения, в формате ГГММДД.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5942">6 digits representing date of birth in the format YYMMDD</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5943">4 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5943">4 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5944">1 контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5944">1 check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5945">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5945">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5946">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5946">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5947">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5947">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5948">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5948">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5949">функция Func_pesel_identification_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5949">The function Func_pesel_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5950">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_pesel_identification_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5950">A keyword from Keyword_pesel_identification_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5951">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5951">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5952">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5952">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5953">функция Func_pesel_identification_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5953">The function Func_pesel_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5954">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5954">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Poland National ID (PESEL) -->
      <Entity id="E3AAF206-4297-412F-9E06-BA8487E22456" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_pesel_identification_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_pesel_identification_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_pesel_identification_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5960">ниеповтарзалнинумер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5960">niepowtarzalnynumer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5961">НР. PESEL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5961">nr.-pesel</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5962">НР — PESEL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5962">nr-pesel</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5963">Нумер идентификацижни</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5963">numer identyfikacyjny</span></span>

## <a name="poland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5966">Номер паспорта для Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5966">Poland passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5967">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в тип конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5967">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5968">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5968">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5969">две буквы и семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5969">two letters and seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5970">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5970">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5971">Две буквы (без учета регистра), за которыми следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5971">Two letters (not case sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5972">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5972">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5973">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5973">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5974">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5974">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5975">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5975">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5976">функция Func_polish_passport_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5976">The function Func_polish_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5977">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5977">A keyword from Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5978">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5978">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Poland Passport Number -->
<Entity id="03937FB5-D2B6-4487-B61F-0F8BFF7C3517" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number" />
      </Pattern>
</Entity>
</Version>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5979">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5979">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5980">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5980">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span></span>

## <a name="poland-regon-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5985">Номер РЕГОНа Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5985">Poland REGON number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5986">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5986">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5987">девять цифр или номер из 14 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5987">nine digit or 14 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5988">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5988">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5989">девять цифр или 14 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5989">nine digit or 14-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5990">девять цифр или</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5990">nine digits or</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5991">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5991">nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5992">дискрецион</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5992">hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5993">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5993">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5994">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5994">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5995">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5995">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5996">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5996">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5997">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5997">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5998">Функция Func_polish_regon_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5998">The function Func_polish_regon_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-5999">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_polish_regon_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-5999">A keyword from Keywords_polish_regon_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6000">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6000">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6001">Функция Func_polish_regon_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6001">The function Func_polish_regon_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Polish REGON Number  -->
      <Entity id="fc87b421-f437-4f8b-b739-29a735ead0d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_regon_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_polish_regon_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_regon_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="poland-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6018">Идентификационный номер для таможенного учета Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6018">Poland tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6019">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6019">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6020">11 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6020">11 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6021">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6021">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6022">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6022">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6023">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6023">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6024">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6024">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6025">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6025">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6026">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6026">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6027">Функция  `Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6027">The function  `Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6028">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6028">A keyword from  `Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
  
```xml
      <!-- Poland Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="1ff28b4d-40f2-49e9-b677-9606a88e2bca" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-citizen-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6058">Номер карточки с префиксом "Португалия"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6058">Portugal citizen card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6059">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6059">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6060">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6060">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6061">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6061">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6062">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6062">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6063">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6063">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6064">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6064">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6065">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6065">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6066">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6066">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6067">регулярное выражение Regex_portugal_citizen_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6067">The regular expression Regex_portugal_citizen_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6068">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_portugal_citizen_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6068">A keyword from Keyword_portugal_citizen_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Portugal Citizen Card Number -->
<Entity id="91a7ece2-add4-4986-9a15-c84544d81ecd" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_citizen_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_portugal_citizen_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6088">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Португалия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6088">Portugal driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6089">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6089">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6090">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6090">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6091">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь чисел в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6091">two letters followed by a seven numbers in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6092">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6092">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6093">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр со специальными символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6093">two letters followed by seven numbers with special characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6094">две буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6094">two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6095">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6095">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6096">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6096">six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6097">пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6097">a space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6098">одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6098">one digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6099">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6099">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6100">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6100">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6101">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6101">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6102">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6102">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6103">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6103">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6104">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6104">A keyword from  `Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6120">Номер паспорта для Португалия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6120">Portugal passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6121">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6121">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6122">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6122">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6123">одна буква, за которой следуют шесть цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6123">one letter followed by six digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6124">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6124">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6125">одна буква, за которой следуют шесть цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6125">one letter followed by six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6126">одна буква (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6126">one letter (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6127">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6127">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6128">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6128">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6129">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6129">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6130">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6130">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6131">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6131">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6132">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6132">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6133">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6133">A keyword from  `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6134">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6134">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6135">Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6135">Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6136">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6136">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6137">номер паспорта для португальского языка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6137">portuguese passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6138">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6138">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6139">нúмеро Do пассапорте</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6139">número do passaporte</span></span>

## <a name="portugal-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6140">Идентификационный номер для налога на Португалия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6140">Portugal tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6141">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6141">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6142">девять цифр с необязательными пробелами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6142">nine digits with optional spaces</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6143">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6143">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6144">3 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6144">3 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6145">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6145">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6146">3 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6146">3 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6147">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6147">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6148">3 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6148">3 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6149">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6149">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6150">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6150">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6151">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6151">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6152">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6152">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6153">Функция  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6153">The function  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6154">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6154">A keyword from  `Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6155">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6155">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6156">Функция  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6156">The function  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Portugal Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="65372402-3131-4f1e-9983-4439841d1f15" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6167">идентификационный номер налога</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6167">tax identification number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6169">налог без</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6169">tax no</span></span>

## <a name="romania-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6181">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Румыния</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6181">Romania driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6182">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6182">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6183">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6183">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6184">один символ, за которым следуют восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6184">one character followed by eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6185">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6185">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6186">один символ, за которым следуют восемь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6186">one character followed by eight digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6187">одна буква (без учета регистра) или цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6187">one letter (not case-sensitive) or digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6188">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6188">eight digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6189">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6189">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6190">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6190">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6191">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6191">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6192">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6192">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6193">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6193">The regular expression  `Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6194">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6194">A keyword from  `Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
