## <a name="romania-personal-numeric-code-cnp"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6210">Персональный числовой код Румыния (КНП)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6210">Romania personal numeric code (CNP)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6211">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6211">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6212">13 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6212">13 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6213">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6213">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6214">1 цифра из 1-9</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6214">1 digit from 1-9</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6215">6 цифр, представляющих дату рождения (ГГММДД)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6215">6 digits representing date of birth (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6216">2 цифры, которые могут быть 01-52 или 99</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6216">2 digits which can be 01-52 or 99</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6217">4 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6217">4 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6218">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6218">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6219">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6219">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6220">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6220">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6221">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6221">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6222">Функция  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6222">The function  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6223">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6223">A keyword from  `Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6224">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6224">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6225">Функция  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6225">The function  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Romania Personal Numerical Code (CNP) -->
      <Entity id="eb5fa399-fe28-4c67-8188-d63a616ed89c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="romania-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6276">Номер паспорта для Румыния</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6276">Romania passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6277">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6277">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6278">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6278">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6279">восемь или девять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6279">eight or nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6280">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6280">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6281">восемь или девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6281">eight or nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6282">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6282">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6283">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6283">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6284">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6284">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6285">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6285">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6286">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6286">The regular expression  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6287">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6287">A keyword from  `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6288">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6288">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_romania_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6289">Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6289">Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6290">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6290">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6291">номер паспорта для румынского языка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6291">romanian passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6292">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6292">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6293">нумăрул паșапортулуи</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6293">numărul pașaportului</span></span>


## <a name="russia-passport-number-domestic"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6294">Номер паспорта для России (Россия)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6294">Russia passport number domestic</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6295">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6295">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6296">номер из десяти цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6296">ten digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6297">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6297">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6298">номер из десяти цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6298">ten digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6299">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6299">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6300">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6300">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6301">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6301">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6302">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6302">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6303">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6303">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6304">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6304">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6305">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6305">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6306">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6306">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6307">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6307">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6308">Регулярное выражение Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6308">The regex Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6309">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6309">A keyword from Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Russian Passport Number Domestic -->
      <Entity id="76ec2f5d-cedb-48e1-8070-1998794af445" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6310">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6310">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_russia_passport_number_domestic"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6311">Keyword_russia_passport_number_domestic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6311">Keyword_russia_passport_number_domestic</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6312">номер паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6312">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6313">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6313">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6314">службу #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6314">passport #</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6316">пасспортно #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6316">passportno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6317">пасспортнумбер #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6317">passportnumber#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6318">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6318">паспорт нет</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6319">Идентификатор паспорт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6319">паспорт id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6320">поссийской паспорт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6320">pоссийской паспорт</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6321">пусский номер паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6321">pусский номер паспорта</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6322">паспорт #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6322">паспорт#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6323">паспортид #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6323">паспортid#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6324">номер паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6324">номер паспорта</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6325">номерпаспорта #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6325">номерпаспорта#</span></span>


## <a name="russia-passport-number-international"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6326">Номер паспорта для России Международная</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6326">Russia passport number international</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6327">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6327">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6328">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6328">nine digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6329">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6329">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6330">девять цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6330">nine digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6331">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6331">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6332">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6332">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6333">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6333">seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6334">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6334">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6335">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6335">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6336">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6336">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6337">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6337">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6338">Регулярное выражение Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_International находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6338">The regex Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_International finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6339">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6339">A keyword from Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Russian Passport Number International -->
      <Entity id="ac5f4878-75e4-4b82-af2d-02e13ea9f411" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_International" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6348">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6348">паспорт нет</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6349">Идентификатор паспорт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6349">паспорт id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6350">поссийской паспорт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6350">pоссийской паспорт</span></span>

## <a name="saudi-arabia-national-id"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6356">Национальный идентификатор для Саудовской Аравии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6356">Saudi Arabia National ID</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6357">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6357">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6358">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6358">ten digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6359">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6359">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6360">десять последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6360">ten consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6361">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6361">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6362">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6362">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6363">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6363">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6364">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6364">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6365">регулярное выражение Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6365">The regular expression Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6366">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6366">A keyword from Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Saudi Arabia National ID -->
<Entity id="8c5a0ba8-404a-41a3-8871-746aa21ee6c0" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6367">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6367">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6368">Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6368">Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6369">Identification Card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6369">Identification Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6370">I card number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6370">I card number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6371">ID number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6371">ID number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6372">الوطنية الهوية بطاقة رقم</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6372">الوطنية الهوية بطاقة رقم</span></span> 

   
## <a name="singapore-national-registration-identity-card-nric-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6373">Номер национальной идентификационной карточки для регистрации (NRIC), Сингапур</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6373">Singapore national registration identity card (NRIC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6374">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6374">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6375">девять букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6375">nine letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6376">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6376">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6377">девять букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6377">nine letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6378">буква "F", "G", "S" или "T" (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6378">the letter "F", "G", "S", or "T" (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6379">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6379">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6380">цифра алфавитной проверки</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6380">an alphabetic check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6381">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6381">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6382">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6382">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6383">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6383">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6384">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6384">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6385">регулярное выражение Regex_singapore_nric находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6385">The regular expression Regex_singapore_nric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6386">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_singapore_nric;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6386">A keyword from Keyword_singapore_nric is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6387">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6387">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6388">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6388">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6389">регулярное выражение Regex_singapore_nric находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6389">The regular expression Regex_singapore_nric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6390">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6390">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Singapore National Registration Identity Card (NRIC) Number -->
<Entity id="cead390a-dd83-4856-9751-fb6dc98c34da" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_singapore_nric"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_singapore_nric"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_singapore_nric"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="slovakia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6401">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Словакия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6401">Slovakia driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6402">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6402">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6403">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6403">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6404">один символ, за которым следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6404">one character followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6405">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6405">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6406">один символ, за которым следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6406">one character followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6407">одна буква (без учета регистра) или цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6407">one letter (not case-sensitive) or digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6408">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6408">seven digits</span></span> 
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6409">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6409">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6410">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6410">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6411">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6411">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6412">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6412">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6413">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6413">The regular expression  `Regex_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6414">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6414">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovaknia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="slovakia-personal-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6430">Словакия персональный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6430">Slovakia personal number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6431">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6431">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6432">девять или десять цифр, содержащих необязательную обратную косую черту</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6432">nine or ten digits containing optional backslash</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6433">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6433">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6434">6 цифр, представляющих дату рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6434">6 digits representing date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6435">Необязательная косая черта (/)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6435">optional slash (/)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6436">3 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6436">3 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6437">1 обязательная контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6437">1 optional check digit</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6438">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6438">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6439">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6439">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6440">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6440">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6441">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6441">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6442">Функция  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6442">The function  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6443">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6443">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6444">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6444">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6445">Функция  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6445">The function  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovakia Personal Number -->
      <Entity id="951c26b7-3b35-4f73-924b-15dd599cb9ab" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
    </Version>
```

## <a name="slovakia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6492">Словакия — номер паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6492">Slovakia passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6493">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6493">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6494">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6494">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6495">одна цифра или буква, за которой следуют семь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6495">one digit or letter followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6496">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6496">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6497">одна цифра или буква (без учета регистра), за которой следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6497">one digit or letter (not case sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6498">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6498">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6499">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6499">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6500">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6500">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6501">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6501">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6502">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6502">The regular expression  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6503">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6503">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6504">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6504">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6505">Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6505">Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6506">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6506">passport number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6508">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6508">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6509">číсло Пасу</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6509">číslo pasu</span></span>


## <a name="slovenia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6510">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Словения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6510">Slovenia driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6511">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6511">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6512">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6512">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6513">девять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6513">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6514">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6514">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6515">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6515">nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6516">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6516">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6517">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6517">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6518">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6518">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6519">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6519">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6520">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6520">The regular expression  `Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6521">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6521">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="slovenia-unique-master-citizen-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6537">Словения уникальный номер хозяина</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6537">Slovenia Unique Master Citizen Number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6538">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6538">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6539">13 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6539">13 digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6540">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6540">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6541">13 цифр в указанном шаблоне:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6541">13 digits in the specified pattern:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6542">семь цифр, которые соответствуют дате рождения (ДДММЛЛЛ), где "ЛЛЛ" соответствует последним трем цифрам года рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6542">seven digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMLLL) where "LLL" corresponds to the last three digits of the birth year</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6543">две цифры, соответствующие области рождения "50"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6543">two digits that correspond to the area of birth "50"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6544">три цифры, которые соответствуют сочетанию пола и серийного номера для людей, которые приставили один и тот же день (000-499 для пола и 500-999 для розетки)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6544">three digits that correspond to a combination of gender and serial number for persons born on the same day (000-499 for male and 500-999 for female)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6545">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6545">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6546">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6546">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6547">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6547">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6548">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6548">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6549">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6549">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6550">Функция  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6550">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6551">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6551">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6552">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6552">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6553">Функция  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6553">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Unique Master Citizen Number -->
      <Entity id="68948b27-803d-41e4-adf1-13e05eb541bb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6554">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6554">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6563">Идентификатор наЦионална</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6563">nacionalna id</span></span>

national id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6565">national id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6570">персональный код</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6570">personal code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6571">персональный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6571">personal number</span></span>

## <a name="slovenia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6581">Номер паспорта для Словения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6581">Slovenia passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6582">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6582">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6583">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6583">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6584">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6584">two letters followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6585">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6585">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6586">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6586">two letters followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6587">буква "P"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6587">the letter "P"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6588">одна прописная буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6588">one uppercase letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6589">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6589">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6590">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6590">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6591">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6591">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6592">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6592">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6593">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6593">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6594">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6594">The regular expression  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6595">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6595">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6596">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6596">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6597">Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6597">Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6598">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6598">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6599">номер паспорта для словенского языка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6599">slovenian passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6600">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6600">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6601">Список потнега šтевилка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6601">številka potnega lista</span></span>

## <a name="slovenia-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6602">Идентификационный номер для налога на Словения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6602">Slovenia tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6603">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6603">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6604">восемь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6604">eight digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6605">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6605">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6606">одна цифра из 1-9</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6606">one digit from 1-9</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6607">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6607">six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6608">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6608">one check digit</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6609">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6609">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6610">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6610">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6611">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6611">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6612">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6612">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6613">Функция  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6613">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6614">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6614">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6615">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6615">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6616">Функция  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6616">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="e47b071e-c352-4d70-8241-8c215ad65505" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6626">идентификационный номер налога</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6626">tax identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6627">налог без #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6627">tax no#</span></span>

## <a name="south-africa-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6640">Идентификационный номер Южно-Африканского Республика</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6640">South Africa identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6641">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6641">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6642">13 цифр, которые могут содержать пробелы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6642">13 digits that may contain spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6643">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6643">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6644">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6644">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6645">шесть цифр в формате ГГММДД Дата рождения;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6645">six digits in the format YYMMDD which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6646">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6646">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6647">Индикатор гражданства, состоящих из одной цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6647">a single-digit citizenship indicator</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6648">цифра "8" или "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6648">the digit "8" or "9"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6649">одна цифра контрольной суммы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6649">one digit which is a checksum digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6650">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6650">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6651">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6651">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6652">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6652">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6653">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6653">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6654">функция Func_south_africa_identification_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6654">The function Func_south_africa_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6655">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_south_africa_identification_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6655">A keyword from Keyword_south_africa_identification_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6656">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6656">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- South Africa Identification Number -->
<Entity id="e2adf7cb-8ea6-4048-a2ed-d89eb65f2780" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_africa_identification_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_south_africa_identification_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6657">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6657">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_south_africa_identification_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6658">Keyword_south_africa_identification_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6658">Keyword_south_africa_identification_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6659">Identity card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6659">Identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6660">ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6660">ID</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6661">Процедура</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6661">Identification</span></span> 
   
## <a name="south-korea-resident-registration-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6662">Регистрационный номер резидентной Южной Кореи</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6662">South Korea resident registration number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6663">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6663">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6664">13 цифр, содержащих дефис.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6664">13 digits containing a hyphen</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6665">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6665">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6666">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6666">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6667">шесть цифр в формате ГГММДД Дата рождения;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6667">six digits in the format YYMMDD which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6668">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6668">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6669">одна цифра, определяемая столетием и пол</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6669">one digit determined by the century and gender</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6670">код региона рождения из четырех цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6670">four-digit region-of-birth code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6671">одна цифра, используемая для различения людей, для которых предыдущие числа идентичны</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6671">one digit used to differentiate people for whom the preceding numbers are identical</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6672">контрольная цифра.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6672">a check digit.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6673">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6673">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6674">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6674">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6675">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6675">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6676">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6676">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6677">функция Func_south_korea_resident_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6677">The function Func_south_korea_resident_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6678">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_south_korea_resident_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6678">A keyword from Keyword_south_korea_resident_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6679">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6679">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6680">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6680">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6681">функция Func_south_korea_resident_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6681">The function Func_south_korea_resident_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6682">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6682">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- South Korea Resident Registration Number -->
<Entity id="5b802e18-ba80-44c4-bc83-bf2ad36ae36a" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_korea_resident_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_south_korea_resident_number"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_korea_resident_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_south_korea_resident_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6684">Keyword_south_korea_resident_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6684">Keyword_south_korea_resident_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6685">National ID card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6685">National ID card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6688">ррн</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6688">RRN</span></span>

## <a name="spain-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6690">Номер водительского удостоверения для Испании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6690">Spain driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6691">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6691">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6692">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6692">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6693">восемь цифр, за которыми следует один символ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6693">eight digits followed by one character</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6694">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6694">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6695">восемь цифр, за которыми следует один символ:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6695">eight digits followed by one character:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6696">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6696">eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6697">одна цифра или буква (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6697">one digit or letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6698">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6698">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6699">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6699">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6700">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6700">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6701">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6701">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6702">Функция  `Func_spain_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6702">The function  `Func_spain_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6703">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6703">A keyword from  `Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="spain-dni"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6740">Испания, DNI</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6740">Spain DNI</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6741">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6741">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6742">восемь цифр, за которыми следует один символ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6742">eight digits followed by one character</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6743">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6743">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6744">семь цифр, за которыми следует один символ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6744">seven digits followed by one character</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6745">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6745">eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6746">Необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6746">An optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6747">один проверочный символ (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6747">one check letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6748">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6748">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6749">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6749">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6750">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6750">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6751">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6751">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6752">Функция  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` или `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6752">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6753">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card"` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6753">A keyword from  `Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card"` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6754">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6754">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-6755">Функция  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` или `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-6755">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 

    
```xml
      <!-- Spain DNI -->
      <Entity id="8e6251b9-47b4-40e8-a42b-0f80876be192" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
