numéro de sécurité sociale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7208">numéro de sécurité sociale</span></span>

   
## <a name="taiwan-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7209">Национальный идентификационный номер для Тайваня</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7209">Taiwan national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7210">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7210">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7211">одна буква (на английском языке), за которой следуют девять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7211">one letter (in English) followed by nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7212">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7212">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7213">одна буква (на английском языке), за которой следуют девять цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7213">one letter (in English) followed by nine digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7214">одна буква (на английском языке, без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7214">one letter (in English, not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7215">цифра "1" или "2"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7215">the digit "1" or "2"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7216">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7216">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7217">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7217">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7218">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7218">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7219">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7219">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7220">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7220">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7221">функция Func_taiwanese_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7221">The function Func_taiwanese_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7222">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_taiwanese_national_id;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7222">A keyword from Keyword_taiwanese_national_id is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7223">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7223">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7224">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7224">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7225">функция Func_taiwanese_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7225">The function Func_taiwanese_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7226">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7226">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwanese National ID -->
<Entity id="4C7BFC34-8DD1-421D-8FB7-6C6182C2AF03" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_taiwanese_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwanese_national_id" />
      </Pattern>
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
         <IdMatch idRef="Func_taiwanese_national_id" />
       </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7227">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7227">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_taiwan_national_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7228">Keyword_taiwan_national_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7228">Keyword_taiwan_national_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7229">身份證字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7229">身份證字號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7230">身份證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7230">身份證</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7231">身份證號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7231">身份證號碼</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7232">身份證號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7232">身份證號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7233">身分證字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7233">身分證字號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7234">身分證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7234">身分證</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7235">身分證號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7235">身分證號碼</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7236">身份證號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7236">身份證號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7237">身分證統一編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7237">身分證統一編號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7238">國民身分證統一編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7238">國民身分證統一編號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7239">簽名</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7239">簽名</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7240">蓋章</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7240">蓋章</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7241">簽名或蓋章</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7241">簽名或蓋章</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7242">簽章</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7242">簽章</span></span>   
   
## <a name="taiwan-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7243">Номер паспорта для Тайваня</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7243">Taiwan passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7244">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7244">Format</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7245">номер биометрического паспорта: девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7245">biometric passport number: nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7246">номер биометрической службы Passport: девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7246">non-biometric passport number: nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7247">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7247">Pattern</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7248">номер биометрического паспорта:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7248">biometric passport number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7249">символ "3"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7249">the character "3"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7250">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7250">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7251">номер биометрической службы Passport:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7251">non-biometric passport number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7252">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7252">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7253">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7253">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7254">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7254">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7255">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7255">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7256">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7256">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7257">регулярное выражение Regex_taiwan_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7257">The regular expression Regex_taiwan_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7258">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_taiwan_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7258">A keyword from Keyword_taiwan_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwan Passport Number -->
<Entity id="e7251cb4-4c2c-41df-963e-924eb3dae04a" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_taiwan_passport"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwan_passport"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7259">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7259">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_taiwan_passport"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7260">Keyword_taiwan_passport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7260">Keyword_taiwan_passport</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7261">ROC passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7261">ROC passport number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7262">Passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7262">Passport number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7263">Passport no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7263">Passport no</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7264">Passport Num</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7264">Passport Num</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7265">Passport #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7265">Passport #</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7266">护照</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7266">护照</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7267">中華民國護照</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7267">中華民國護照</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7268">Zhōnghuá Mínguó hùzhào</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7268">Zhōnghuá Mínguó hùzhào</span></span>
   
## <a name="taiwan-resident-certificate-arctarc-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7269">Номер сертификата резидента (ARC/TARC) для Тайваня</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7269">Taiwan resident certificate (ARC/TARC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7270">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7270">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7271">десять букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7271">ten letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7272">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7272">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7273">десять букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7273">ten letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7274">две буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7274">two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7275">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7275">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7276">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7276">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7277">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7277">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7278">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7278">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7279">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7279">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7280">регулярное выражение Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7280">The regular expression Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7281">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7281">A keyword from Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwan Resident Certificate (ARC/TARC) -->
<Entity id="48269fec-05ea-46ea-b326-f5623a58c6e9" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7282">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7282">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7283">Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7283">Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7284">Resident Certificate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7284">Resident Certificate</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7285">Resident Cert</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7285">Resident Cert</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7286">Resident Cert.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7286">Resident Cert.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7287">Identification card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7287">Identification card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7288">Alien Resident Certificate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7288">Alien Resident Certificate</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7289">ARC</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7289">ARC</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7290">Taiwan Area Resident Certificate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7290">Taiwan Area Resident Certificate</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7291">TARC</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7291">TARC</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7292">居留證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7292">居留證</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7293">外僑居留證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7293">外僑居留證</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7294">台灣地區居留證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7294">台灣地區居留證</span></span> 

## <a name="thai-population-identification-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7295">Код идентификации для тайского заполнения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7295">Thai population identification code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7296">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7296">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7297">13 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7297">13 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7298">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7298">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7299">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7299">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7300">Первая цифра не равна нулю или девять</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7300">first digit is not zero  or nine</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7301">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7301">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7302">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7302">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7303">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7303">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7304">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7304">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7305">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7305">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7306">Функция Func_Thai_Citizen_Id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7306">The function Func_Thai_Citizen_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7307">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7307">A keyword from Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7308">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7308">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7309">Функция Func_Thai_Citizen_Id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7309">The function Func_Thai_Citizen_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Thai Citizen ID -->
-<Entity id="44ca9e86-ead7-4c5d-884a-e2eaa401515e" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7310">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7310">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_thai_citizen_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7311">Keyword_thai_citizen_Id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7311">Keyword_thai_citizen_Id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7312">ID Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7312">ID Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7313">Идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7313">Identification Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7314">บัตรประชาชน</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7314">บัตรประชาชน</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7315">รหัสบัตรประชาชน</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7315">รหัสบัตรประชาชน</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7316">บัตรประชาชน</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7316">บัตรประชาชน</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7317">รหัสบัตรประชาชน</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7317">รหัสบัตรประชาชน</span></span>
  
## <a name="turkish-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7318">Турецкий национальный идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7318">Turkish national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7319">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7319">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7320">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7320">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7321">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7321">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7322">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7322">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7323">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7323">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7324">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7324">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7325">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7325">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7326">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7326">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7327">Функция Func_Turkish_National_Id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7327">The function Func_Turkish_National_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7328">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_Turkish_National_Id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7328">A keyword from Keyword_Turkish_National_Id is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7329">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7329">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7330">Функция Func_Turkish_National_Id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7330">The function Func_Turkish_National_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Turkish National Identity -->
-<Entity id="fb621f20-3876-4cfc-acec-8c8e73ca32c7" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Turkish_National_Id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_Turkish_National_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Turkish_National_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7331">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7331">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_turkish_national_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7332">Keyword_turkish_national_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7332">Keyword_turkish_national_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7333">TC Кимлик No</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7333">TC Kimlik No</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7334">TC Кимлик нумарасı</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7334">TC Kimlik numarası</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7335">Ватандаşлıк нумарасı</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7335">Vatandaşlık numarası</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7336">Ватандаşлıк нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7336">Vatandaşlık no</span></span>

## <a name="uk-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7337">Королевств</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7337">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7338">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7338">driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7339">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в тип конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7339">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7340">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7340">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7341">Сочетание 18 букв и цифр в указанном формате.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7341">Combination of 18 letters and digits in the specified format</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7342">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7342">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7343">18 букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7343">18 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7344">пять букв (без учета регистра) или цифра 9 вместо буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7344">five letters (not case sensitive) or the digit "9" in place of a letter</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7345">одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7345">one digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7346">пять цифр в формате даты ММДДИ для даты рождения (седьмой символ увеличивается на 50, если драйвер — гнездо, то есть 51 – 62, а не с 01 – 12)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7346">five digits in the date format MMDDY for date of birth (7th character is incremented by 50 if driver is female, i.e. 51 to 62 instead of 01 to 12)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7347">две буквы (без учета регистра) или цифра "9" вместо буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7347">two letters (not case sensitive) or the digit "9" in place of a letter</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7348">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7348">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7349">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7349">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7350">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7350">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7351">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7351">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7352">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7352">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7353">функция Func_uk_drivers_license находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7353">The function Func_uk_drivers_license finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7354">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_drivers_license;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7354">A keyword from Keyword_uk_drivers_license is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7355">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7355">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="f93de4be-d94c-40df-a8be-461738047551" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_drivers_license" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_drivers_license" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7356">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7356">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_uk_drivers_license"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7357">Keyword_uk_drivers_license</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7357">Keyword_uk_drivers_license</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7358">двла</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7358">DVLA</span></span>

## <a name="uk-electoral-roll-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7373">Королевств</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7373">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7374">номер рулона електорал</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7374">electoral roll number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7375">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7375">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7376">две буквы, за которыми следуют 1-4 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7376">two letters followed by 1-4 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7377">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7377">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7378">две буквы (без учета регистра), за которыми следуют 1-4 номера</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7378">two letters (not case sensitive) followed by 1-4 numbers</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7379">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7379">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7380">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7380">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7381">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7381">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7382">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7382">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7383">регулярное выражение Regex_uk_electoral находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7383">The regular expression Regex_uk_electoral finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7384">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_electoral.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7384">A keyword from Keyword_uk_electoral is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. Electoral Number -->
<Entity id="a3eea206-dc0c-4f06-9e22-aa1be3059963" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_uk_electoral" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_electoral" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7385">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7385">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_uk_electoral"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7386">Keyword_uk_electoral</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7386">Keyword_uk_electoral</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7387">council nomination</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7387">council nomination</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7388">nomination form</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7388">nomination form</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7389">electoral register</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7389">electoral register</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7390">electoral roll</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7390">electoral roll</span></span>

   
## <a name="uk-national-health-service-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7391">Королевств</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7391">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7392">Национальный номер службы работоспособности</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7392">national health service number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7393">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7393">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7394">10–17 цифр, разделенных пробелами.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7394">10-17 digits separated by spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7395">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7395">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7396">10-17 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7396">10-17 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7397">либо три, либо десять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7397">either three or ten digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7398">пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7398">a space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7399">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7399">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7400">пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7400">a space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7401">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7401">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7402">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7402">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7403">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7403">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7404">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7404">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7405">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7405">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7406">Функция Func_uk_nhs_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7406">The function Func_uk_nhs_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7407">Верно одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7407">One of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7408">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_nhs_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7408">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7409">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_nhs_number1;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7409">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number1 is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7410">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7410">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7411">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7411">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. NHS Number -->
<Entity id="3192014e-2a16-44e9-aa69-4b20375c9a78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nhs_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number1" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="uk-national-insurance-number-nino"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7429">Королевств</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7429">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7430">Национальный страховой номер (Нино)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7430">national insurance number (NINO)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7431">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в тип конфиденциальной конфиденциальной информации ЕС Идентификаитон и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7431">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU National Identificaiton Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7432">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7432">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7433">семь символов или девять символов, разделенных пробелами или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7433">seven characters or nine characters separated by spaces or dashes</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7434">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7434">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7435">два возможных шаблона:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7435">two possible patterns:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7436">две буквы (допустимые Нинос используют только определенные символы в этом префиксе, которые пропускаются при проверке этого шаблона; без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7436">two letters (valid NINOs use only certain characters in this prefix, which this pattern validates; not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7437">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7437">six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7438">"A", "B", "C", или "'D" (например, префикс, в суффиксе допускаются только определенные символы; без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7438">either 'A', 'B', 'C', or 'D' (like the prefix, only certain characters are allowed in the suffix; not case sensitive)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7439">OR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7439">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7440">две буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7440">two letters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7441">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7441">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7442">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7442">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7443">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7443">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7444">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7444">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7445">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7445">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7446">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7446">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7447">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7447">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7448">значение "A", "B", "C" или "'D"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7448">either 'A', 'B', 'C', or 'D'</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7449">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7449">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7450">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7450">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7451">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7451">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7452">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7452">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7453">функция Func_uk_nino находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7453">The function Func_uk_nino finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7454">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_nino.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7454">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nino is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7455">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7455">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7456">функция Func_uk_nino находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7456">The function Func_uk_nino finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7457">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_nino не находится.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7457">No keyword from Keyword_uk_nino is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. NINO -->
<Entity id="16c07343-c26f-49d2-a987-3daf717e94cc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nino" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nino" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>    
     <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nino" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nino" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7458">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7458">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="uk-unique-taxpayer-reference-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7479">Королевств</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7479">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7480">Уникальный номер ссылки налогоплательщика</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7480">Unique Taxpayer Reference Number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7481">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7481">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7482">10 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7482">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
 
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7483">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7483">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7484">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7484">10 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7485">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7485">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7486">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7486">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7487">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7487">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7488">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7488">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7489">Функция  `Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7489">The function  `Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7490">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7490">A keyword from  `Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- U.K. Unique Taxpayer Reference Number -->
      <Entity id="ad4a8116-0db8-439a-b545-6d967642f0ec" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="us-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7510">Номер банковского счета США</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7510">U.S. bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7511">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7511">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7512">8-17 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7512">8-17 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7513">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7513">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7514">8–17 последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7514">8-17 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7515">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7515">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7516">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7516">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7517">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7517">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7518">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7518">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7519">регулярное выражение Regex_usa_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7519">The regular expression Regex_usa_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7520">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_usa_Bank_Account.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7520">A keyword from Keyword_usa_Bank_Account is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.S. Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="a2ce32a8-f935-4bb6-8e96-2a5157672e2c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_usa_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_usa_Bank_Account" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="us-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7550">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера США</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7550">U.S. driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7551">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7551">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7552">Зависит от штата.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7552">Depends on the state</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7553">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7553">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7554">зависит от штата — например, Нью Йорк:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7554">depends on the state -- for example, New York:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7555">девять цифр, отформатированных как DDD DDD DDD, будут совпадают.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7555">nine digits formatted like ddd ddd ddd will match.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7556">девять цифр, такие как ццццццццц, не совпадают.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7556">nine digits like ddddddddd will not match.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7557">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7557">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7558">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7558">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7559">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7559">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7560">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7560">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7561">функция Func_new_york_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7561">The function Func_new_york_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7562">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7562">A keyword from Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7563">обнаружено ключевое слово из списка Keyword_us_drivers_license.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7563">A keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7564">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7564">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7565">функция Func_new_york_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7565">The function Func_new_york_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7566">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7566">A keyword from Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7567">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7567">A keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7568">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_us_drivers_license не находится.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7568">No keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="dfeb356f-61cd-459e-bf0f-7c6d28b458c6 patternsProximity="300">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_york_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_new_york_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license" />
    </Pattern>
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_york_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_new_york_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="us-individual-taxpayer-identification-number-itin"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7666">Индивидуальный идентификационный номер налогоплательщика (SHAREPOINTВ) для США</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7666">U.S. individual taxpayer identification number (ITIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7667">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7667">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7668">девять цифр, начинающиеся с цифры "9" и содержащие "7" или "8" в качестве четвертой цифры, при необходимости отформатированные с помощью пробелов или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7668">nine digits that start with a "9" and contain a "7" or "8" as the fourth digit, optionally formatted with spaces or dashes</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7669">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7669">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7670">форматируемые</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7670">formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7671">цифра "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7671">the digit "9"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7672">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7672">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7673">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7673">a space or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7674">"7" или "8"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7674">a "7" or "8"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7675">цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7675">a digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7676">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7676">a space, or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7677">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7677">four digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7678">неформатированные</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7678">unformatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7679">цифра "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7679">the digit "9"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7680">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7680">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7681">"7" или "8"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7681">a "7" or "8"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7682">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7682">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7683">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7683">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7684">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7684">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7685">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7685">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7686">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7686">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7687">Функция Func_formatted_itin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7687">The function Func_formatted_itin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7688">Верно по меньшей мере одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7688">At least one of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7689">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_itin;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7689">A keyword from Keyword_itin is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7690">функция Func_us_address находит адрес в правильном формате;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7690">The function Func_us_address finds an address in the right date format.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7691">функция Func_us_date находит дату в правильном формате.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7691">The function Func_us_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7692">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_itin_collaborative.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7692">A keyword from Keyword_itin_collaborative is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7693">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7693">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7694">Функция Func_unformatted_itin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7694">The function Func_unformatted_itin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7695">Верно по меньшей мере одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7695">At least one of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7696">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_itin_collaborative;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7696">A keyword from Keyword_itin_collaborative is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7697">функция Func_us_address находит адрес в правильном формате;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7697">The function Func_us_address finds an address in the right date format.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7698">функция Func_us_date находит дату в правильном формате.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7698">The function Func_us_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.S. Individual Taxpayer Identification Number (ITIN) -->
<Entity id="e55e2a32-f92d-4985-a35d-a0b269eb687b" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_formatted_itin" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_itin" />
          <Match idRef="Func_us_address" />
          <Match idRef="Func_us_date" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_itin_collaborative" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_itin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_itin" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_itin_collaborative" />
          <Match idRef="Func_us_address" />
          <Match idRef="Func_us_date" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7699">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7699">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7701">дубликат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7701">taxpayer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7703">tax identification</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7703">tax identification</span></span>

## <a name="us-social-security-number-ssn"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7719">Номер социального страхования (SSN) США</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7719">U.S. social security number (SSN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7720">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7720">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7721">девять цифр, которые могут быть в форматированном или неформатированном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7721">nine digits, which may be in a formatted or unformatted pattern</span></span>

> [!NOTE]
> <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7722">Есть SSN выдан до середины 2011 г., он отличается строгим форматированием, при котором определенные части номера должны входить в указанные диапазоны (при этом нет контрольной суммы).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7722">If issued before mid-2011, an SSN has strong formatting where certain parts of the number must fall within certain ranges to be valid (but there's no checksum).</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7723">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7723">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7724">четыре функции ищут служб SSNs в четырех различных шаблонах:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7724">four functions look for SSNs in four different patterns:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7725">Func_ssn находит SSN со строгим форматированием с тире или пробелами, выданные до 2011 г. (ццц-цц-цццц ИЛИ ццц цц цццц);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7725">Func_ssn finds SSNs with pre-2011 strong formatting that are formatted with dashes or spaces (ddd-dd-dddd OR ddd dd dddd)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7726">Func_unformatted_ssn находит SSN со строгим форматированием, выданные до 2011 г. (без форматирования в виде девяти последовательных цифр — ццццццццц);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7726">Func_unformatted_ssn finds SSNs with pre-2011 strong formatting that are unformatted as nine consecutive digits (ddddddddd)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7727">Func_randomized_formatted_ssn находит SSN с тире или пробелами, выданные после 2011 г. (ццц-цц-цццц ИЛИ ццц цц цццц);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7727">Func_randomized_formatted_ssn finds post-2011 SSNs that are formatted with dashes or spaces (ddd-dd-dddd OR ddd dd dddd)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7728">Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn находит SSN без форматирования в виде девяти последовательных цифр, выданные после 2011 г. (ццццццццц).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7728">Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn finds post-2011 SSNs that are unformatted as nine consecutive digits (ddddddddd)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7729">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7729">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7730">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7730">No</span></span>


### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7731">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7731">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7732">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7732">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7733">Функция Func_ssn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7733">The function Func_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7734">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ssn.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7734">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7735">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7735">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7736">Функция Func_unformatted_ssn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7736">The function Func_unformatted_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7737">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ssn.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7737">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7738">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7738">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7739">Функция Func_randomized_formatted_ssn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7739">The function Func_randomized_formatted_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7740">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ssn.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7740">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7741">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 55 % верно обнаружила этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в пределах ближайших 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7741">A DLP policy is 55% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7742">Функция Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7742">The function Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7743">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ssn.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7743">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>


```xml
<!-- U.S. Social Security Number (SSN) -->
  <Entity id="a44669fe-0d48-453d-a9b1-2cc83f2cba77" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_randomized_formatted_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="55">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
  </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7744">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7744">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_ssn"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7745">Keyword_ssn</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7745">Keyword_ssn</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7746">Номер адаптера SSA</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7746">SSA Number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7749">социальное обеспечение безопасности #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7749">social security#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7750">социальное страхование нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7750">social security no</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7755">SSN #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7755">SSN#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7756">НН #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7756">SS#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7757">SSID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7757">SSID</span></span>
   
## <a name="us--uk-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7758">США/ВЕЛИКОБРИТАНИЯ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7758">U.S. / U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7759">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7759">passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7760">Великобритания</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7760">The U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7761">Объект типа конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта доступен в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7761">passport number sensitive information type entity is available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7762">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7762">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7763">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7763">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7764">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7764">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7765">девять последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7765">nine consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7766">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7766">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7767">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7767">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7768">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7768">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7769">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7769">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7770">функция Func_usa_uk_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7770">The function Func_usa_uk_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7771">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7771">A keyword from Keyword_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="178ec42a-18b4-47cc-85c7-d62c92fd67f8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_usa_uk_passport" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7772">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7772">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_passport"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7773">Keyword_passport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7773">Keyword_passport</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7774">Passport Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7774">Passport Number</span></span>

## <a name="ukraine-passport-domestic"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7792">Украина Passport Россия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7792">Ukraine passport domestic</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7793">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7793">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7794">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7794">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7795">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7795">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7796">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7796">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7797">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7797">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7798">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7798">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7799">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7799">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7800">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7800">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7801">Регулярное выражение Regex_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7801">The regex Regex_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7802">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7802">A keyword from Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Ukraine Passport Domestic -->
      <Entity id="1817a540-221f-4459-9202-3bd78b81d803" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7803">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7803">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7805">паспорт "Украина"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7805">ukraine passport</span></span>

## <a name="ukraine-passport-international"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7811">Украина Passport International</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7811">Ukraine passport international</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7812">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7812">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7813">буквенно-цифровой шаблон из восьми символов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7813">eight-character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7814">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7814">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7815">8-значный буквенно-цифровой шаблон:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7815">eight-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7816">две буквы или цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7816">two letters or digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7817">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7817">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7818">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7818">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7819">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7819">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7820">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7820">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7821">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7821">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7822">Регулярное выражение Regex_Ukraine_Passport_International находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7822">The regex Regex_Ukraine_Passport_International finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7823">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_International.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7823">A keyword from Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_International is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Ukraine Passport International -->
      <Entity id="cfbe032d-22e0-4f28-ab68-d66e9641f1e2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Ukraine_Passport_International"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_International"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="2c8ba-7824">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c8ba-7824">Keywords</span></span>
